Ch3%3EWhat%20size%20is%20best%20for%20a%20gaming%20monitor%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ideal%20size%20for%20your%20gaming%20monitor%20mostly%20depends%20on%20how%20far%20you%20plan%20to%20sit%20from%20your%20computer%20and%20what%20types%20of%20games%20you%20plan%20to%20play.%20For%20example%2C%20competitive%20gamers%20should%20opt%20for%2024%20or%2027-inch%20monitors%2C%20because%20they%20tend%20to%20sit%20relatively%20close%20to%20the%20screen%20and%20can%20benefit%20from%20the%20higher%20refresh%20rates%20that%20are%20typically%20available%20on%20monitors%20of%20that%20size.%20Players%20who%20prefer%20adventure%20games%20or%20immersive%20sports%20and%20racing%20simulations%20can%20opt%20for%20larger%20monitors%20that%20rival%20TV%20sizes%20at%2032-inches%20and%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20recommendation%20is%20to%20measure%20the%20distance%20from%20your%20usual%20gaming%20seat%20to%20your%20screen%3B%20if%20it's%20two%20feet%20or%20less%20we%20recommend%20a%2027-inch%20monitor%20or%20smaller%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20further%20than%20two%20feet%20away%2C%20go%20for%20a%2032-inch%20monitor%20or%20larger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20curved%20monitors%20better%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20best%20gaming%20monitors%20are%20curved%20to%20provide%20a%20better%20viewing%20angle%3B%20this%20can%20be%20helpful%20when%20sitting%20close%20to%20large%20screens.%20However%2C%20a%20curved%20screen%20alone%20won't%20make%20the%20picture%20appear%20better.%20Some%20people%20may%20prefer%20a%20standard%20flat%20screen%20for%20tasks%20like%20photo%20and%20video%20editing%2C%20to%20ensure%20the%20monitor's%20curve%20doesn't%20distort%20their%20perception%20of%20on-screen%20images.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonitor%20curves%20are%20measured%20based%20on%20their%20radius%3B%20the%20smaller%20the%20radius%2C%20the%20deeper%20the%20curve%20in%20the%20monitor.%20So%2C%20a%201000R%20monitor%20is%20more%20curved%20than%20a%201500R%20monitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20resolution%20is%20best%20for%20a%20gaming%20monitor%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20resolution%20for%20your%20monitor%20will%20ultimately%20depend%20on%20your%20PC%20or%20console%20and%20what%20games%20you%20like%20to%20play.%20PlayStation%205%20and%20Xbox%20Series%20consoles%20are%20designed%20to%20output%20at%204K%20resolution%2C%20while%20the%20Nintendo%20Switch%20maxes%20out%20at%201080p.%20For%20PC%20gamers%2C%20resolution%20will%20depend%20on%20the%20strength%20of%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-a-graphics-card%5C%22%3Egraphics%20card%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Most%20computers%20can%20run%20games%20at%201080p%2C%20while%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-gaming-pc%5C%22%3Ebest%20gaming%20PCs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-gaming-laptop%5C%22%3Ebest%20gaming%20laptops%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20have%20the%20power%20to%20run%20at%201440p%20and%20even%204K.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigher%20resolution%20typically%20means%20more%20visual%20detail%2C%20so%20you'll%20usually%20want%20to%20run%20at%20the%20highest%20option%20possible.%20Some%20competitive%20gamers%20prefer%20to%20limit%20their%20resolution%20to%201080p%20so%20that%20gameplay%20runs%20at%20a%20higher%20frame%20rate%2C%20which%20can%20reduce%20delay%20and%20improve%20reaction%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20does%20refresh%20rate%20impact%20a%20gaming%20monitor%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ERefresh%20rate%20denotes%20how%20many%20times%20a%20display%20updates%20the%20image%20you%20see%20on-screen%20per%20second%3B%20a%2060Hz%20monitor%20will%20display%2060%20individual%20frames%20per%20second%2C%20while%20a%20144Hz%20monitor%20will%20show%20144%20frames%20per%20second%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20higher%20refresh%20rates%20make%20animations%20appear%20smoother%20and%20you'll%20experience%20less%20delay%20when%20trying%20to%20react%20to%20things%20on%20screen%2C%20especially%20if%20your%20gaming%20PC%20can%20run%20games%20faster%20than%2060%20frames%20per%20second.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERefresh%20rate%20is%20also%20slightly%20less%20important%20with%20consoles%2C%20because%20they're%20designed%20to%20work%20with%20TVs%20with%20lower%20refresh%20rates%2C%20and%20games%20are%20often%20locked%20to%2060%20or%2030%20frames%20per%20second.%20PlayStation%205%20and%20Xbox%20Series%20X%20are%20capable%20of%20playing%20some%20games%20at%20120Hz%20with%20variable%20refresh%20rate%2C%20while%20the%20Nintendo%20Switch%20is%20limited%20to%2060Hz%20and%20has%20no%20VRR%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20low%20end%2C%20the%20best%20gaming%20monitors%20tend%20to%20start%20at%20a%20refresh%20rate%20of%20144Hz%2C%20while%20premium%20models%20can%20have%20refresh%20rates%20as%20high%20as%20360Hz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20variable%20refresh%20rate%20(VRR)%2C%20AdaptiveSync%2C%20and%20G-Sync%20work%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EVariable%20refresh%20rate%20(VRR)%20is%20a%20feature%20that%20works%20to%20match%20your%20PC%20or%20console's%20frame%20rate%20with%20the%20monitor's%20refresh%20rate%2C%20which%20prevents%20screen%20tearing%20or%20other%20issues%20that%20can%20arise%20when%20the%20frame%20rate%20and%20refresh%20rate%20aren't%20even.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdaptive%20Sync%20is%20a%20general%20term%20used%20to%20describe%20VRR%20compatibility.%20G-Sync%20is%20a%20version%20of%20VRR%20technology%20that%20works%20specifically%20with%20graphics%20cards%20from%20Nvidia%2C%20while%20AMD%20graphics%20cards%20call%20their%20VRR%20tech%20FreeSync.%20The%20Adaptive%20Sync%20feature%20is%20still%20designed%20to%20work%20with%20graphics%20cards%20from%20Nvidia%20and%20AMD%2C%20even%20if%20the%20monitor%20isn't%20fully%20G-Sync%20or%20FreeSync%20certified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20gaming%20monitors%20include%20speakers%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20gaming%20monitors%20do%20include%20speakers%2C%20which%20can%20be%20convenient%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20separate%20set%20of%20speakers%20and%20you%20prefer%20to%20game%20without%20headphones.%20However%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20most%20computer%20monitor%20speakers%20usually%20isn't%20worth%20the%20extra%20money%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20you're%20better%20off%20buying%20an%20affordable%20set%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-computer-speakers%5C%22%3EPC%20speakers%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%2460%20or%20less.With%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20none%20of%20our%20picks%20for%20the%20best%20gaming%20monitors%20include%20built-in%20speakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-gaming-monitor%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697839052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6532d98fbe9edfa8eda67b7b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-gaming-monitor%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20gaming%20monitors%20have%20fast%20refresh%20rates%2C%20high%20resolutions%2C%20and%20bright%20colors.%20These%20are%20our%20top%20picks%20from%20brands%20like%20LG%2C%20Asus%2C%20and%20Samsung.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kwebb%40businessinsider.com%20(Kevin%20Webb)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-gaming-monitor%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IOC%20hits%20back%20at%20Putin%20claim%20of%20'ethnic%20discrimination'%20against%20Russia's%20potential%20Olympic%20athletes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697838978000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104593640%2Cimgsize-14148.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fioc-hits-back-at-putin-claim-of-ethnic-discrimination-against-russias-potential-olympic-athletes%2Far