y%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20there's%20room%20for%20concern%20that%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20could%20expand%20into%20a%20broader%20Middle%20Eastern%20clash%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20that%20this%20would%20fuel%20a%20prolonged%20oil%20price%20spike%2C%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20the%20fighting%20spreads%20beyond%20Israel%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20territories%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20result%20in%20a%20prolonged%20oil%20price%20spike%26quot%3B%20they%20predicted.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20tangible%20signs%20that%20high%20oil%20prices%20amplified%20by%20surging%20borrowing%20costs%20and%20depreciating%20EM%20currencies%20began%20to%20erode%20fuel%20consumption.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOil%20demand%20in%20Taiwan%2C%20Thailand%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20South%20Korea%20has%20fallen%2C%20while%20total%20crude%20imports%20into%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20are%20also%20down%2C%20according%20to%20JPMorgan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20on%20top%20of%20observations%20JPMorgan%20had%20previously%20made%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.in%2Fstock-market%2Fnews%2Foil-prices-drop-6-as-worries-mount-over-demand-destruction%2Farticleshow%2F104168686.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemand%20destruction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20high%20summer%20prices%20and%20the%20end%20of%20peak%20travel%20season%20pushed%20consumers%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20geopolitical%20fears%20have%20sent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Foil-price%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3EBrent%3C%2Fa%3E%20crude%20into%20the%20%2490%20range%2C%20the%20bank%20sees%20this%20as%20relatively%20restrained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeyond%20the%20short-term%20spike%20induced%20by%20geopolitics%2C%20our%20base%20case%20for%20oil%20remains%20that%20large%20inventory%20draws%20observed%20in%203Q23%20will%20transition%20to%20a%20largely%20balanced%20market%20in%204Q23%20(our%20model%20oscillates%20between%20100%20kbd%20build%20and%20100%20kbd%20draw)%20with%20Brent%20exiting%20the%20year%20at%20%2486%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20note%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20JPMorgan%20doesn't%20see%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20spreading%20to%20a%20more%20regional%20conflict%2C%20saying%20that%20Israel%2C%20Iran%2C%20the%20US%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20and%20the%20UAE%20have%20strong%20incentives%20to%20keep%20conflict%20contained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20evidenced%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20top%20energy%20producers%20like%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20UAE%20haven't%20supported%20an%20oil%20embargo%20on%20Israel%20or%20its%20allies%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20oil%20prices%20rarely%20experienced%20long-term%20turmoil%20during%20most%20of%20Israel's%20past%20conflicts%2C%20JPMorgan%20said.%20While%20the%20country%20went%20through%2010%20instances%20of%20major%20military%20clashes%20since%201967%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20them%20resulted%20in%20a%20momentary%20price%20jump%2C%20given%20early%20apprehensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEventually%2C%20oil%20prices%20tended%20to%20gradually%20stabilize%20and%20decline%2C%20resulting%20in%20Brent%20actually%20trading%20at%20a%20discount%20to%20its%20fundamentally-derived%20fair%20value.%20In%20these%20cases%2C%20the%20near-term%20supply-demand%20balance%20and%20the%20resulting%20change%20in%20oil%20inventories%20have%20been%20a%20more%20important%20factor%20to%20follow%20than%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20note%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20the%201973%20Yom%20Kippur%20war%20saw%20longer%20lasting%20impacts%2C%20given%20that%20it%20led%20to%20a%20Saudi%20oil%20embargo%20against%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBroadening%20this%20outlook%20to%20other%20Middle%20Eastern%20regions%2C%20military%20operations%20haven't%20often%20led%20to%20significant%20consequences%20on%20markets.%20Prices%20saw%20little%20change%20in%202011's%20Syrian%20c