0gag%20order%2C%20prohibiting%20personal%20attacks%20on%20court%20staff%20involved%20in%20the%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjudge-threatens-to-hold-donald-trump-in-contempt-after-deleted-post-is-found-on-campaign-website%2Farticleshow%2F104592979.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjudge-threatens-to-hold-donald-trump-in-contempt-after-deleted-post-is-found-on-campaign-website%2Famp_articleshow%2F104592979.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjudge-threatens-to-hold-donald-trump-in-contempt-after-deleted-post-is-found-on-campaign-website%2Famp_articleshow%2F104592979.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Combat%20video%20shows%20what%20Ukraine%20says%20are%20its%20special%20ops%20forces%20destroying%20enemy%20armor%2C%20capturing%20the%20cost%20of%20Russia's%20new%20assaults%20in%20the%20east%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russian%20armored%20vehicles%20moving%20near%20Avdiivka.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6532bd9a96908fd7cdb4162c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221580%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20armored%20vehicles%20moving%20near%20Avdiivka.%3Cp%3EScreengrab%2FSpecial%20Operations%20Forces%20of%20Ukraine%20via%20Telegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EUkraine's%20military%20published%20new%20footage%20showing%20what%20it%20says%20is%20the%20destruction%20of%20Russian%20armor.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20video%20captures%20Russian%20tank%20and%20vehicle%20losses%20near%20Avdiivka%2C%20Kyiv's%20special%20ops%20forces%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EAvdiivka%2C%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%2C%20is%20one%20area%20where%20Moscow%20recently%20launched%20a%20renewed%20assault.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20combat%20footage%20shared%20by%20Ukraine's%20military%20on%20Friday%20captures%20what%20it%20says%20is%20the%20destruction%20of%20Russian%20tanks%20and%20armor%2C%20highlighting%20the%20increasing%20toll%20of%20Moscow's%20new%20assaults%20in%20the%20east.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20Special%20Operations%20Forces%20(SSO)%20said%20it%20detected%20Russian%20armor%20heading%20toward%20Avdiivka%2C%20a%20small%20city%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine's%20Donetsk%20region%20that's%20currently%20surrounded%20on%20three%20sides%20by%20Russian-occupied%20territory.%20It's%20one%20area%20where%20Moscow's%20forces%20recently%20launched%20a%20%26quot%3Brenewed%20offensive%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20US%20officials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SSO%20said%20it%20used%20a%20combination%20of%20first-person%20view%20(FPV)%20drones%2C%20US-provided%20Javelin%20anti-tank%20guided%20missiles%2C%20and%20mortars%20to%20stop%20the%20advancing%20Russians%20and%20destroyed%20four%20armored%20personnel%20carriers%2C%20two%20tanks%2C%20and%20an%20unspecified%20number%20of%20soldiers.%20Insider%20was%20unable%20to%20immediately%20verify%20the%20details%20of%20the%20video%20or%20Moscow's%20troop%20and%20equipment%20losses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20of%20the%20fierce%20fighting%20%E2%80%94%20which%20the%20SSO%20posted%20to%20Telegram%20and%20X%2C%20the%20platform%20formally%20known%20as%20Twitter%20%E2%80%94%20several%20explosions%20can%20be%20seen%20around%20the%20apparent%20Russian%20armor%20force%20as%20it%20attempts%20to%20maneuver%20through%20open%20fields.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20an%20armored%20vehicle%20appears%20to%20bump%20into%20another%20and%20nudge%20it%20forward%20before%20they%20are%20both%20engulfed%20in%20a%20fireball.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22undefined%5C%22%20data-cards%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%94SPECIAL%20OPERATIONS%20FORCES%20OF%20UKRAINE%20(%40SOF_UKR)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmims%2Fstatuses%2F1715303518410596595%5C%22%3EOctober%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%20Spokesperson%20John%20Kirby%20told%20reporters%20on%20October%2013%20that%20over%20the%20previous%20few%20days%20Russia%20had%20launched%20a%20%26quot%3Brenewed%20offensive%26quot%3B%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%2C%20including%20around%20Avdiivka%20and%20Lyman%2C%20a%20city%20just%20under%20100%20miles%20to%20the%20north.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20move%20was%20not%20a%20surprise%2C%20given%20that%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20not%20given%20up%20on%20his%20ultimate%20goal%20of%20conquering%20Ukrainian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKirby%20said%20at%20that%20time%20that%20amid%20Russia's%20offensive%2C%20its%20military%20appeared%20to%20again%20be%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-bloody-human-wave-tactics-ukraine-white-house-says-2023-10%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bhuman%20wave%20tactics%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20sending%20poorly%20trained%20and%20equipped%20soldiers%20straight%20onto%20the%20battlefield%20without%20preparation.%20This%20gruesome%20strategy%20is%20not%20new%20to%20Moscow%3B%20it%20relied%20heavily%20on%20this%20method%20during%20the%20brutal%20fighting%20that%20took%20place%20this%20past%20winter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRussia%20continues%20to%20show%20no%20regard%20for%20the%20lives%20of%20its%20own%20soldiers%2C%20willingly%20sacrificing%20them%20in%20pursuit%20of%20Putin's%20goals%2C%20while%20Ukraine%20continues%20to%20fight%20bravely%2C%20effectively%2C%20and%20smartly%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirby%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20would%20add%20that%20we%20have%20seen%20the%20Ukrainians%20work%20very%20hard%20to%20repel%20these%20offensive%20maneuvers%2C%20and%20they%20appear%20to%20have%20done%20just%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20at%20the%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%2C%20a%20Washington-based%20think%20tank%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20Thursday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Frussian-offensive-campaign-assessment-october-19-2023%5C%22%3Eanalysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Russia%20lost%20dozens%20of%20tanks%20and%20armored%20vehicles%20during%20the%20initial%20days%20of%20its%20assault%20around%20Avdiivka.%20The%20experts%20also%20cited%20a%20Ukrainian%20military%20official%20who%20reported%20several%20Russian%20aircraft%20losses%20and%20said%20that%20the%20official's%20announcements%20suggests%20that%20Moscow%20is%20paying%20a%20high%20cost%20to%20prop%20up%20its%20fight%20around%20Avdiivka.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BContinued%20materiel%20losses%20will%20likely%20continue%20to%20slow%20down%20the%20Russian%20pace%20of%20advance%20in%20the%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20these%20experts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Frussian-offensive-campaign-assessment-october-19-2023%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22undefined%5C%22%20data-cards%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%94Jimmy%20Rushton%20(%40JimmySecUK)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmims%2Fstatuses%2F1715326009061384345%5C%22%3EOctober%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20SSO%20said%20Friday%20on%20Telegram%20that%20while%20Russia%20is%20engaged%20in%20offensive%20actions%20around%20Avdiivka%20and%20is%20relentless%20in%20its%20attempts%20to%20surround%20the%20city%2C%20Kyiv%20has%20managed%20to%20%26quot%3Bfirmly%26quot%3B%20defend%20the%20area%20and%20inflict%20%26quot%3Bconsiderable%20losses%26quot%3B%20on%20Moscow's%20forces%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20recent%20dest