Fwww.sec.gov%2Fix%3Fdoc%3D%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F909832%2F000119312522027035%2Fd497640d8k.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappointed%3C%2Fa%3E%20president%20and%20chief%20operating%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20almost%20certainly%20paves%20the%20way%20for%20Mr.%20Vachris%20to%20succeed%20current%20CEO%20Craig%20Jelinek%2C%26quot%3B%20Morgan%20Stanley%20retail%20analyst%20Simeon%20Gutman%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.supermarketnews.com%2Fexecutive-changes%2Fcostco-elevates-ron-vachris-president-coo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enote%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BIf%20Vachris%20is%20appointed%20CEO%2C%20he%20would%20be%20the%20third%20CEO%20in%20Costco's%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20company%20confirmed%20that%20Vachris%20had%20been%20working%20%26quot%3Bhand%20in%20hand%26quot%3B%20with%20Jelinek%20on%20a%20transition%20when%20it%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-ceo-craig-jelinek-bio-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJelinek%20would%20end%20his%2011-year%20run%3C%2Fa%3E%20effective%20January%201%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%C2%A0have%20total%20confidence%20in%20Ron%20and%20feel%20that%20we%20are%20fortunate%20as%20a%20Company%20to%20have%20an%20executive%20of%20his%20caliber%20to%20succeed%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Jelinek%20said%20in%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestor.costco.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-details%2F2023%2FCostco-Wholesale-Corporation-Announces-Craig-Jelinek-Will-Step-Down-as-CEO-Ron-Vachris-Elected-as-New-CEO-And-Quarterly-Cash-Dividend-Declared%2Fdefault.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20Vachris'%20history%20with%20the%20company%20goes%20back%20much%20farther%20than%20his%20most%20recent%20role%20%E2%80%94%20four%20decades%2C%20in%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201982%2C%20while%20majoring%20in%20business%20as%20a%20comm