unilateral%E2%80%9D%2C%20asserting%20that%20it%20merely%20aimed%20to%20seek%20parity%20in%20diplomatic%20missions%20between%20Ottawa%20and%20Delhi%2C%20rather%20than%20extending%20it%20to%20outposts%20in%20other%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Canadian%20foreign%20minister%20M%C3%A9lanie%20Joly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-confirms-withdrawal-of-41-diplomats-from-india-visa-processing-time-to-go-up%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2041%20Canadian%20diplomats%20left%20India%2C%20leaving%20only%2021%20diplomats%20manning%20the%20high%20commission%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20the%20three%20consulates%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Bangalore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20she%20declared%20the%20suspension%20of%20in-person%20services%20at%20the%20three%20consulates.%20Although%20the%20Canadian%20high%20commission%20in%20New%20Delhi%20will%20still%20accept%20applications%2C%20Joly%20noted%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cservice%20standards%20for%20residents%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%20would%20experience%20disruptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanadian%20media%20also%20quoted%20officials%20mentioned%20in%20a%20background%20briefing%20that%2027%20officials%20from%20the%20immigration%20department%20had%20been%20recalled%2C%20leaving%20only%20five%20personnel%20remaining%20in%20India.%20This%20downsizing%20is%20expected%20to%20result%20in%20a%20backlog%20of%20approximately%2017%2C500%20applications%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theglobeandmail.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticle-canada-diplomats-leave-india%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20Globe%20and%20Mail%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20issued%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37201%2FParity%2Bin%2BCanadian%2Bdiplomatic%2Bpresence%2Bin%2BIndia%5C%22%3Eofficial%20response%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday%20afternoon%20that%20predominantly%20contested%20Joly%E2%80%99s%20portrayal%20of%20the%20Indian%20intention%20to%20revoke%20diplomatic%20immunity%20for%20all%20but%2021%20Canadian%20diplomats%20as%20a%20breach%20of%20international%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELate%20on%20Friday%20night%2C%20Indian%20official%20sources%20told%20reporters%20in%20the%20background%20that%20clarified%20that%20they%20had%20not%20been%20pursuing%20a%20reduction%20in%20staffing%20levels%20at%20the%20three%20Canadian%20consulates%2C%20which%20was%20the%20rationale%20behind%20Ottawa%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20suspend%20in-person%20consulate%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20Indian%20sources%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cparity%20has%20been%20sought%20in%20the%20diplomatic%20representations%20of%20our%20Missions%20in%20Ottawa%20and%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20impact%20on%20Canadian%20diplomatic%20strength%20in%20their%20Consulates%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mumbai%20and%20Chandigarh.%20The%20Canadian%20decision%20to%20cease%20operations%20of%20their%20three%20consulates%20in%20India%2C%20is%20unilateral%2C%20and%20not%20related%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20parity%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETill%20now%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20has%20never%20publicly%20said%20that%20the%20demand%20for%20parity%20was%20only%20limited%20to%20the%20main%20diplomatic%20missions%20in%20the%20capital%20cities.%20India%20has%20a%20high%20commission%20in%20Ottawa%20and%20two%20consulates%20in%20Vancouver%20and%20Toronto.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F37134%2Ftranscript%2Bof%2Bweekly%2Bmedia%2Bbriefing%2Bby%2Bthe%2Bofficial%2Bspokesperson%2Bseptember%2B21%2B2023%5C%22%3EOn%20September%2021%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20MEA%20spokesperson%20had%20first%20announced%20that%20India%20had%20conveyed%20to%20the%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CCanadian%20government%20that%20there%20should%20be%20parity%20in%20strength%20and%20rank%20equivalence%20in%20our%20diplomatic%20presence%2C%20in%20mutual%20diplomatic%20presence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F37165%2Ftranscript%2Bof%2Bweekly%2Bmedia%2Bbriefing%2Bby%2Bthe%2Bofficial%2Bspokesperson%2Boctober%2B05%2B2023%5C%22%3EOctober%205%20media%20briefing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20MEA%20was%20asked%20whether%20it%20anticipated%20that%20the%20demand%20for%20parity%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20deterioration%20in%20visa%20services%2C%20particularly%20in%20states%20like%20Punjab%20and%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20had%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6let%20me%20also%20clarify%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20parity%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20up%20to%20the%20Canadian%20side%20who%20they%20choose%20to%20staff%20their%20high%20commission%20with.%20So%20I%20would%20refer%20you%20to%20them%2C%20for%20any%20details.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20our%20concerns%20are%20related%20to%20ensuring%20parity%20in%20diplomatic%20presence.%20And%20again%2C%20as%20I%20said%2C%20why%3F%20And%20I%20think%2C%20you%20know%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20been%20our%20focus%20very%20clearly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficial%20sources%20also%20confirmed%20Joly%E2%80%99s%20statement%20that%20New%20Delhi%20had%20given%20a%20deadline%20of%20October%2010%2C%20which%20was%20extended%20till%20October%2020.%20%E2%80%9CAttempts%20by%20Canada%20to%20portray%20this%20as%20an%20%E2%80%98arbitrary%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98overnight%E2%80%99%20decision%20is%20factually%20inaccurate%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said%20on%20Friday%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20extension%20was%20given%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdetails%20and%20modalities%20of%20implementation%2C%20including%20the%20list%20of%20Canadian%20diplomats%20who%20would%20continue%20to%20be%20accorded%20diplomatic%20immunities%20and%20privileges%20were%20being%20worked%20out%20in%20consultation%20with%20the%20Canadian%20side%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20side%20also%20stated%20that%20Canada%20had%20been%20told%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20order%20to%20limit%20the%20size%20of%20the%20Missions%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Ottawa%2C%20only%20a%20specific%20number%20of%20diplomats%20as%20per%20parity%20would%20continue%20to%20enjoy%20diplomatic%20privileges%20and%20immunities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERepeating%20the%20argument%20made%20in%20the%20official%20press%20release%2C%20sources%20said%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20action%20was%20within%20the%20provisions%20of%20Article%2011.1%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flegal.un.org%2Filc%2Ftexts%2Finstruments%2Fenglish%2Fconventions%2F9_1_1961.pdf%5C%22%3EVienna%20Convention%20on%20Diplomatic%20Relations%3C%2Fa%3E%20(VCDR)%20which%20allows%20the%20receiving%20state%20to%20limit%20the%20size%20of%20a%20diplomatic%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CArticle%2011.1%20has%20been%20used%20in%20the%20past%20by%20other%20countries%20on%20many%20occasions%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20foreign%20minister%20had%20claimed%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cunilateral%20revocation%20of%20diplomatic%20privileges%20and%20immunities%20is%20contrary%20to%20international%20law%2C%20including%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20Diplomatic%20Relations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20this%20action%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fglobal-affairs%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2Fstatement-on-expulsion-of-canadian-diplomats-by-the-government-of-india.html%5C%22%3Ecompletely%20unreasonable%20and%20escalatory%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20had%20said%20that%20India%20accredited%20each%20and%20every%20one%20of%20the%20Canadian%20diplomats%20they%20are%20now%20expelling.%20%E2%80%9CDiplomatic%20immunities%20should%20be%20respected%20and%20cannot%20be%20unilaterally%20revoked%20by%20a%20host%20country.%20If%20we%20allow%20this%20norm%20to%20be%20broken%2C%20no%20diplomat%20anywhere%20would%20be%20safe.%20As%20such%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20Canada%20will%20continue%20to%20respect%20diplomatic%20norms%20and%20not%20reciprocate%20this%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Joly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExpanding%20upon%20the%20argument%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20achieving%20parity%20did%20not%20infringe%20upon%20the%20VCDR%2C%20Indian%20sources%20additionally%20contended%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flaws-lois.justice.gc.ca%2Feng%2Facts%2Ff-29.4%2Fpage-1.html%23h-234995%5C%22%3ECanadian%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20empowers%20Ottawa%20to%20provide%20%E2%80%9Ccomparable%E2%80%9D%20treatment%20to%20foreign%20diplomats%20and%20to%20%E2%80%9Cwithdraw%20any%20of%20the%20privileges%2C%20immunities%20and%20benefits%20accorded%20or%20granted%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697826541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21121523%2FUntitled-design-3-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-calls-canadas-consulate-move-unilateral-clarifies-parity-only-for-diplomats-in-capitals%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canadian%20foreign%20minister%20M%C3%A9lanie%20Joly%20said%20in-person%20services%20at%20its%20three%20consulates%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20Mumbai%20have%20been%20suspended%2C%20following%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20its%2041%20diplomats%20from%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-calls-canadas-consulate-move-unilateral-clarifies-parity-only-for-diplomats-in-capitals%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20sticks%20to%20stand%20on%20crypto%20assets%20ban%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697826375000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F06%2Ffull%2F1696615716-0074.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Frbi-governor-shaktikanta-das-sticks-to-position-on-crypto-asset-ba