0brought%20to%20attention%20by%20Tikok%20user%20ytkingkhan%2C%20who%20tested%20the%20phrase%20on%20his%20Instagram%20account.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20after%20the%20TikTok%20user's%20video%20went%20viral%20online%2C%20Meta%20issued%20an%20apology%20for%20adding%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20bios%20of%20some%20Palestinian%20Instagram%20users.%20The%20company%20said%20that%20it%20fixed%20a%20problem%20%26quot%3Bthat%20briefly%20caused%20inappropriate%20Arabic%20translations%26quot%3B%20in%20some%20of%20its%20products.%20%26quot%3BWe%20sincerely%20apologise%20that%20this%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Meta%20spokesperson%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2023%2Foct%2F20%2Finstagram-palestinian-user-profile-bios-terrorist-added-translation-meta-apology%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20this%20comes%20amid%20a%20time%20when%20Meta%20is%20facing%20accusations%20of%20suppressing%20content%20voicing%20support%20for%20Palestinians%20during%20the%20Israel-Gaza%20war.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-67169228%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20several%20users%20have%20stated%20that%20they%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bshadow-banned%26quot%3B%20on%20Instagram%20over%20pro-Palestinian%20posts.%20They%20also%20accused%20the%20social%20media%20company%20of%20demoting%20their%20content%2C%20meaning%20it%20was%20less%20likely%20to%20appear%20in%20others'%20feeds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-says-2-us-hostages-kidnapped-in-october-7-attacks-released-4501211%5C%22%3EReleased%202%20American%20Hostages%20On%20%26quot%3BHumanitarian%20Grounds%26quot%3B%3A%20Hamas%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeta%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20said%20that%20it%20introduced%20several%20measures%20s