or%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fwill-palestine-authorities-pay-hamas-terrorists-families%2Farticleshow%2F104591963.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20Speaking%20Of%20Dynasty%20Is%20Joke%20Of%20The%20Millennium%26quot%3B%3A%20KTR%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20voting%20for%20the%20Telangana%20elections%20just%20over%20a%20month%20away%2C%20the%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20has%20made%20regional%20pride%20the%20centrepiece%20of%20its%20campaign%20amid%20attacks%20of%20corruption%20and%20dynastic%20politics%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress.%20The%20party's%20working%20president%2C%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%2C%20who%20had%20said%20Andhra%20landlords%20were%20the%20villains%20during%20the%20last%20elections%2C%20has%20trained%20his%20guns%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3Eghulams%20%3C%2Fem%3E(servants)%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20the%20Delhi%20%3Cem%3Edurbar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(courtiers)%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20also%20rubbished%20allegations%20from%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20of%20his%20party%20siding%20with%20the%20other%20and%20said%20the%20BRS%20is%20nobody's%20B-team%2C%20but%20Telangana's%20A-team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20statehood%20movement%20of%20Telangana%20was%20predicated%20on%20two%20things%20-%20self-respect%20and%20pride.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20comes%20to%20Hyderabad%20and%20says%20one%20Gujarati%20(Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel)%20relieved%20you%20from%20the%20clutches%20of%20the%20Nizam%20and%20another%20Gujarati%20(PM%20Narendra%20Modi)%20will%20relieve%20you%20from%20KCR%20(Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao's)%20dictatorial%20rule%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rao%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20son%20of%20KCR%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20have%20to%20invoke%20pride%20and%20we%20also%20have%20to%20remind%20people%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Eghulams%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Gujarat%20here%20in%20Telangana%20-%20the%20BJP%20folks%20-%20have%20not%20done%20much%20in%20the%20past%20nine-and-a-half%20years%20and%20we%20have%20to%20speak%20about%20their%20track%20record%20as%20well.%20Same%20is%20the%20case%20with%20the%20Delhi%20%3Cem%3Edurbar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Rahul%20%3Cem%3Ebaba%3C%2Fem%3E%20comes%20here%20and%20starts%20saying%20things%20like%20family%20rule%20and%20dynasty%2C%20which%20probably%20has%20to%20be%20the%20joke%20of%20the%20millennium%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao%2C%20who%20is%20a%20minister%20and%20holds%20the%20information%20technology%20portfolio%2C%20among%20others%2C%20said%20people%20from%20Gujarat%20and%20Delhi%20don't%20do%20their%20homework%20before%20coming%20to%20Telangana%20and%20he%20and%20his%20party%20have%20to%20remind%20them%20from%20time%20to%20time%20that%20the%20Telangana%20statehood%20agitation%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20great%20self-respect.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20most%20important%20tenets%20of%20that%20movement%20was%20pride%2C%20and%20you%20cannot%20come%20and%20insult%20us%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20election-related%20seizures%20in%20Telangana%20touching%20Rs%20243%20crore%20in%20just%20ten%20days%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20blamed%20the%20Congress%20and%20said%20that%20money%20had%20been%20seized%20from%20one%20of%20its%20former%20corporators%20in%20Bengaluru.%20When%20it%20was%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20seizure%20was%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20he%20said%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20have%20common%20businesses%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20few%20builders%20have%20told%20me%20that%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20started%20charging%20an%20extra%20election%20tax%20-%20Rs%20500%20per%20square%20foot%20-%20and%20they%20are%20telling%20th