d-104590269%2Cimgsize-56412.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fswara-bhasker-wonders-who-she-would-protect-her-daughter-if-she-were-born-in-gaza-amid-israel-hamas-conflict%2Farticleshow%2F104590177.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104590177.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESwara%20Bhasker%20expressed%20her%20grief%20and%20concern%20for%20innocent%20lives%20affected%20during%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20in%20an%20emotional%20statement.%20She%20took%20to%20Instagram%20to%20share%20a%20picture%20with%20her%20baby%20girl%20and%20wondered%20how%20she%20would%20protect%20her%20kid%20if%20she%20were%20born%20in%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fswara-bhasker-wonders-who-she-would-protect-her-daughter-if-she-were-born-in-gaza-amid-israel-hamas-conflict%2Farticleshow%2F104590177.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kohli%20Shatters%20Tendulkar's%20Record%2C%20Achieves%20Massive%20Feat%20With%20WC%20Century%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20team%20star%20batter%20Virat%20Kohli%20had%20a%20historic%20outing%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20match%20against%20Bangladesh%20at%20Pune%20on%20Thursday.%20Virat%20smashed%20his%20match-winning%20century%2C%2048th%20in%20ODIs%20and%2078th%20at%20international%20level.%20He%20scored%20103%20runs%20in%2097%20balls%20with%20six%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes.%20His%20runs%20came%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20106.%20With%20this%2C%20he%20is%20just%20one%20away%20from%20levelling%20Sachin%20Tendulkar's%20record%20of%2049%20ODI%20centuries.%20Also%2C%20with%20his%2078th%20international%20ton%2C%20just%2023%20centuries%20are%20left%20for%20him%20to%20overtake%20Sachin's%20record%20of%20100%20international%20centuries.%20Virat%20also%20brought%20up%20his%2026%2C000%20international%20runs%2C%20becoming%20the%20fastest%20to%20do%20so%2C%20in%20just%20567%20innings%2C%20leaving%20behind%20Sachin%20(600%20innings).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20511%20matches%20and%20567%20innings%2C%20Virat%20has%20scored%2026%2C026%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2053.99%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%2079.%20He%20has%20scored%2078%20centuries%20and%20134%20fifties%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%20254*.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20this%2C%20he%20also%20overtook%20Sri%20Lankan%20great%20Mahela%20Jayawardene%20(25%2C957%20runs)%20to%20become%20the%20fourth-leading%20run-scorer%20of%20all%20time%20in%20international%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%2030%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20matches%2C%20Virat%20has%20scored%201%2C289%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2053.70%2C%20with%20three%20centuries%20and%20eight%20fifties%20in%2030%20innings%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%20107.%20He%20is%20the%20fourth-highest%20run-scorer%20in%20WC%20history%2C%20with%20Sachin%20(2%2C278%20runs)%20at%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20World%20Cup%2C%20Virat%20is%20the%20second-highest%20run-scorer.%20In%20four%20innings%2C%20he%20has%20scored%20259%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%20129.50%2C%20with%20one%20century%20and%20two%20fifties%2C%20his%20best%20score%20is%20103*.%20His%20strike%20rate%20is%20around%2090.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20Bangladesh%20opted%20to%20bat%20first%20and%20there%20was%20a%2091-run%20opening%20stand%20between%20Tanzid%20Hasan%20(51%20in%2043%20balls%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20three%20sixes)%20and%20Litton%20Das%20(66%20in%2082%20balls%2C%20with%20seven%20fours).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20that%2C%20Bangladesh%20kept%20losing%20wickets%20at%20regular%20intervals%2C%20though%20important%20knocks%20came%20from%20Mahmudullah%20(46%20in%2036%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%20and%20wicketkeeper-batter%20Mushfiqur%20Rahim%20(38%20in%2046%20balls%2C%20with%20a%20four%20and%20six)%20that%20took%20Bangladesh%20to%20256%2F8%20in%2050%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%20(2%2F38)%20and%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20(2%2F41)%20were%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20India.%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20took%20two%20wickets%20as%20well%20while%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20and%20Shardul%20Thakur%20got%20one%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20chase%20of%20257%2C%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(48%20in%2040%20balls%2C%20with%20seven%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20and%20Shubman%20Gill%20(53%20in%2055%20balls%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20decided%20the%20outcome%20with%20their%20partnership%20itself.%20Virat's%20century%20and%20partnership%20with%20KL%20Rahul%20(34*)%2C%20which%20saw%20some%20entertaining%20running%20between%20the%20wickets%20was%20an%20icing%20on%20the%20cake.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMehidy%20Hasan%20Miraz%20took%20two%20wickets%20for%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20four%20wins%20in%20four%20matches%2C%20India%20is%20in%20the%20second%20spot%20in%20the%20points%20table%20with%20eight%20points.%20New%20Zealand%20is%20at%20the%20top%20with%20a%20better%20net-run-rate.%20Bangladesh%20is%20in%20the%20seventh%20spot%20with%20one%20win%20and%20three%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697816520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fmqm6vdb_ff_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fvirat-kohli-shatters-sachin-tendulkars-record-achieves-massive-feat-with-cricket-world-cup-2023-century-4497856%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20shattered%20Sachin%20Tendulkar's%20record%20to%20achieve%20a%20sensational%20feat%20during%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20match%20against%20Bangladesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%