old%20reporters%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Congress%20behaves%20like%20this%2C%20who%20will%20stand%20with%20them.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20had%20expressed%20unhappiness%20over%20the%20Congress%20not%20allocating%20any%20seat%20to%20his%20party%20despite%20talks%20on%20seat%20sharing%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20suggested%20that%20the%20Congress%20could%20get%20the%20same%20treatment%20from%20his%20party%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%20chief%20had%20said%20his%20party%20leaders%20wouldn't%20have%20answered%20calls%20from%20the%20Congress%20for%20a%20meeting%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20had%20he%20known%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20was%20confined%20to%20the%20national%20level.%20%26quot%3BI%20must%20have%20got%20confused%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20President%20Ajay%20Rai%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20Mr%20Yadav%20cannot%20blame%20the%20Congress%20as%20the%20SP%20released%20its%20list%20of%20candidates%20before%20his%20party%20and%20was%20benefitting%20the%20BJP%20by%20contesting%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20SP%20president%20reiterated%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20should%20have%20clarified%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20tie-up%20in%20the%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPDA%20(Backward%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Alpsankhyak)%20was%20formed%20before%20INDIA.%20On%20various%20occasions%2C%20I%20have%20said%20that%20there%20is%20an%20INDIA%20alliance%20but%20our%20strategy%20is%20PDA%20and%20PDA%20will%20defeat%20NDA.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20leader%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20spoke%20to%20us%20and%20asked%20about%20the%20seats%20we%20wanted%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20I%20shared%20the%20performance%20of%20SP%20in%20various%20elections%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20told%20him%20that%20many%20people%20were%20elected%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20who%20joined%20other%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20reminded%20that%20when%20Congress%20needed%20support%2C%20SP%20MLA%20was%20the%20first%20to%20offer%20support%20and%20government%20was%20formed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20we%20offered%20our%20support%20to%20defeat%20BJP.%20In%20the%20meeting%20that%20continued%20till%201%20am%20in%20the%20night%2C%20they%20assured%20us%20to%20give%20six%20seats.%20But%2C%20when%20they%20declared%20candidates%20on%20all%20seats%2C%20in%20compulsion%2C%20the%20SP%20has%20to%20declare%20candidates%20from%20where%20we%20are%20strong%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20(SP)%20announced%20its%20third%20list%20of%20two%20candidates%20on%20Thursday%20night.%20With%20this%2C%20it%20has%20announced%2033%20candidates%20for%20the%20November%2017%20polls%20to%20the%20230-member%20assembly%20in%20the%20BJP-ruled%20state.%20The%20Congress%20has%20announced%20its%20candidates%20for%20229%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20insiders%20from%20both%20parties%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20agreed%20to%20leave%20six%20seats%20for%20SP%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20but%20the%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20did%20not%20materialise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20if%20you%20were%20not%20ready%20to%20give%20any%20seat%20you%20should%20have%20not%20talked%20to%20us.%20But%2C%20they%20didn't%20give%20any%20information%20to%20us.%20So%2C%20SP%20is%20fighting%20where%20we%20have%20our%20presence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20emotions%20that%20Samajwadis%20have%20with%20Azamgarh%20it%20is%20possible%20Congress%20has%20the%20same%20emotions%20in%20Raebareli%20and%20Amethi.%20We%20have%20never%20commented%20on%20Raebareli%20and%20Amethi%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20SP%20chief%20said%20without%20elaborating.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202018%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20elections%2C%20the%20SP%20won%20one%20seat%20(Bijawar%20in%20Bundelkhand%20region)%20and%20finished%20second%20on%20five%2C%20securing%201.30%20per%20cent%20votes%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20tribal%20Gondwana%20Gantantra%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20grouping%20came%20into%20being%20primarily%20to%20put%20up%20a%20united%20front%20against%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20after%20its%20constituents%20fielded%20candidates%20against%20each%20other%20in%20assembly%20polls%2C%20saying%20the%20opposition%20grouping%20is%20driven%20by%20the%20motto%20of%20%26quot%3Bfriendship%20in%20Delhi%20and%20wrestling%20in%20states%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697814300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F73piqm5_akhilesh-yadav-ani_625x300_25_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-congress-behaves-like-this-akhilesh-yadav-on-madhya-pradesh-poll-row-4500827%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Miffed%20with%20the%20Congress%20over%20the%20failure%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20assembly%20polls%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20on%20Friday%20again%20deprecated%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20ally.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-congress-behaves-like-this-akhilesh-yadav-on-madhya-pradesh-poll-row-4500827%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-congress-behaves-like-this-a