esofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fegypt-peace-summit-may-struggle-to-foster-unity-on-gaza-conflict%2Famp_articleshow%2F104589765.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBI%20Busts%20Network%20With%20Foreign%20Link%20Which%20Scammed%20Indians%20Of%20Rs%20300%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20investigation%20spanning%20over%20a%20year%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20unearthed%20a%20sophisticated%2C%20complex%20network%20involving%20foreign%20elements%20which%20cheated%20Indians%20of%20hundreds%20of%20crores%20by%20luring%20them%20with%20job%20and%20loan%20offers%20as%20well%20as%20fooling%20them%20into%20investing%20in%20Ponzi%20schemes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20complex%20web%20of%20UPI%20accounts%2C%20cryptocurrency%20and%20international%20money%20transfers%20was%20used%20to%20move%20the%20money%20and%20the%20agency%20recently%20carried%20out%20raids%20in%20several%20places%20linked%20to%20the%20suspects%20after%20analysing%20the%20money%20trail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorryingly%2C%20the%20CBI%20investigation%20points%20to%20the%20involvement%20of%20137%20shell%20companies%2C%20many%20of%20which%20were%20registered%20with%20the%20Registrar%20of%20Companies%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20their%20directors.%20Some%20of%20these%20directors%20were%20also%20associated%20with%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20payout%20merchant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20They%20Operated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20CBI%20release%2C%20the%20investigation%20-%20which%20was%20part%20of%20the%20agency's%20operation%20Chakra-II%20-%20began%20in%202022.%20A%20case%20was%20registered%20based%20on%20various%20inputs%2C%20including%20one%20given%20by%20the%20Indian%20Cyber%20Crime%20Coordination%20Centre%20(I4C)%20under%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20the%20fraudsters%20allegedly%20used%20various%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20their%20advertisement%20portals%2C%20encrypted%20chat%20applications%20and%20SMS%20to%20entice%20victims%20with%20promises%20of%20loans%2C%20part-time%20jobs%20and%20investments%20in%20Ponzi%20schemes%20and%20multi-level%20marketing%20initiatives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVictims%20were%20lured%20into%20depositing%20funds%20through%20UPI%20by%20promising%20high%20returns.%20The%20money%20was%20laundered%20through%20a%20complex%20network%20of%20UPI%20accounts%20and%20ultimately%20converged%20into%20cryptocurrency%20or%20gold%20purchases%20using%20falsified%20credentials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20also%20identified%20137%20shell%20companies%20engaged%20in%20fraudulent%20activities%2C%20and%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20these%20were%20registered%20with%20the%20Registrar%20of%20Companies%20in%20Bengaluru.%20After%20intense%20investigations%2C%20the%20directors%20of%20these%20companies%20were%20identified%20and%20some%20of%20these%20were%20also%20found%20to%20be%20linked%20to%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20payout%20merchant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20merchant%20controlled%20around%2016%20bank%20accounts%20where%20Rs%20357%20crore%20was%20funnelled%20and%20the%20money%20was%20then%20transferred%20to%20various%20accounts.%20The%20release%20said%20searches%20were%20conducted%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Cochin%20and%20Gurgaon%20and%20yielded%20substantial%20evidence%2C%20shedding%20light%20on%20the%20alleged%20activities%20of%20the%20shell%20companies'%20directors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EForeign%20Link%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20were%20also%20found%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20a%20foreign%20national.%20While%20investigating%20two%20chartered%20accountants%20from%20Bengaluru%20-%20who%20allegedly%20altered%20directorships%20and%20contact%20information%20associated%20with%20the%20shell%20companies%20-%20searches%20were%20conducted%20on%20their%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20the%20searches%20led%20to%20the%20recovery%20of%20documents%2C%20email%20communications%20and%20WhatsApp%20chats%20revealing%20their%20alleged%20role%20in%20facilitating%20foreign%20national's%20involvement%20in%20the%20fraud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%20investigation%20in%20the%20case%20is%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697814180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ff0s44f3_ransomware-generic-cyber-crime-generic_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcbi-busts-network-with-foreign-link-which-scammed-indians-of-over-rs-300-crore-4500605%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CBI%20has%20unearthed%20a%20sophisticated%20network%20involving%20foreign%20elements%20which%20cheated%20Indians%20of%20hundreds%20of%20crore%20by%20luring%20them%20with%20job%20and%20loan%20offers%20as%20well%20as%20fooling%20them%20into%20investing%20in%20Ponzi%20schemes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcbi-busts-network-with-foreign-link-which-scammed-indians-of-over-rs-300-crore-4500605%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcbi-busts-network-with-foreign-link-which-scammed-indians-of-over-rs-300-crore-4500605%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcbi-busts-network-with-foreign-link-which-scammed-indians-of-over-rs-300-crore-4500605%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paytm%20trims%20losses%20to%20Rs%20290%20crore%20in%20Q2%2C%20total%20income%20increases%208%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697813795000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-06%2F21%2Ffull%2F1687319075-8743.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fpaytm-trims-losses-to-rs-290-crore-in-q2-total-income-increases-8-123102001171_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Noida-based%20fintech's%20total%20income%20rose%208%20per%20cent%20on%20a%20quart