ia-q2-results-net-profit-jumps-90-to-rs-605-crore-123102001047_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fcentral-bank-of-india-q2-results-net-profit-jumps-90-to-rs-605-crore-123102001047_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fcentral-bank-of-india-q2-results-net-profit-jumps-90-to-rs-605-crore-123102001047_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Poonawalla%20Fincorp's%20Q2%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20up%2077%25%20to%20Rs%20230%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697812400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F08%2Ffull%2F1696786897-685.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fpoonawalla-fincorp-s-q2-results-net-profit-up-77-to-rs-230-crore-123102001124_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Net%20Interest%20Margin%20(NIM)%20saw%20an%20improvement%20of%20106%20basis%20points%20to%2011.42%20per%20cent%20from%20the%20year-ago%20period%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fpoonawalla-fincorp-s-q2-results-net-profit-up-77-to-rs-230-crore-123102001124_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fpoonawalla-fincorp-s-q2-results-net-profit-up-77-to-rs-230-crore-123102001124_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fpoonawalla-fincorp-s-q2-results-net-profit-up-77-to-rs-230-crore-123102001124_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20RSS%20Plan%20to%20Eradicate%20Caste%20Is%20Outdated%20and%20Skirts%20the%20Real%20Issues%20of%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20161440%2FF06GwWTWcAEgnoO.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20taking%20a%20stand%20on%20the%20caste%20census%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20has%20declared%20that%20it%20would%20work%20for%20the%20eradication%20of%20caste.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20sarsangchalak%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20talked%20about%20God%20not%20creating%20caste%20but%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmohan-bhagwat-rss-pandit-caste-system%5C%22%3Epundits%20having%20created%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20also%20talked%20about%20the%20need%20for%20reservations%20remaining%20as%20long%20as%20caste%20discrimination%20remains.%20These%20are%20stray%20statements%20that%20the%20RSS%20leaders%20give%20to%20satisfy%20Shudra%2FOBCs%20and%20Dalits%2C%20as%20their%20votes%20are%20crucial%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDattatreya%20Hosabale%2C%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20declared%20that%20the%20organisation%20should%20work%20for%20the%20eradication%20of%20caste.%20On%20October%2011%2C%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20its%20workers%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fanyone-can-enter-a-temple-anywhere-work-to-eradicate-caste-bias-hosabale-123101300116_1.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cany%20person%20has%20the%20right%20to%20enter%20a%20temple%20anywhere%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20also%20urged%20RSS%20cadres%20to%20work%20for%20%E2%80%9Celiminating%20caste-based%20discrimination%20which%20brings%20disrepute%20to%20Hinduism%E2%80%9D.%20He%20was%20reported%20to%20have%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAny%20person%20can%20enter%20any%20temple%2C%20and%20everyone%20has%20the%20right%20to%20fetch%20water%20from%20any%20source%20of%20water.%20We%20must%20not%20tolerate%20such%20discrimination%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste%20or%20untouchability%2C%20because%20it%20brings%20disrepute%20to%20the%20entire%20Hindu%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20media%20reported%20his%20statement%20on%20the%20next%20day%20as%20if%20it%20was%20the%20first%20programme%20to%20eradicate%20caste.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDattatreya%E2%80%99s%20plan%20is%20quite%20outdated.%20His%20plan%20is%20built%20on%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20programme%2C%20which%20did%20not%20have%20any%20value%20for%20caste%20eradication%2C%20then%20or%20now.%20Temple%20entry%20for%20Shudras%2C%20OBCs%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20is%20now%20more%20or%20less%20accepted.%20The%20restrictions%20placed%20on%20Dalits%20for%20fetching%20water%20are%20also%20fewer%20now%2C%20though%20sporadic%20incidents%20still%20happen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20plan%20may%20reduce%20caste-based%20discrimination%20in%20a%20few%20areas%20but%20will%20not%20result%20in%20the%20eradication%20or%20abolition%20of%20caste.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20kind%20of%20typical%20old%20Gandhian%20programme%20does%20not%20suit%20the%20present%20times%20and%20demands%20of%20Shudras%2C%20OBCs%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20Adivasis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20Shudra%2FOBCs%20are%20asking%20for%20now%20is%20a%20caste%20census.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnine-reasons-why-the-bihar-caste-census-could-shake-up-national-politics%5C%22%3EBihar%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20already%20done%20it%20and%20released%20the%20results.%20The%20RSS%20seems%20to%20have%20advised%20the%20BJP-run%20Union%20government%20and%20also%20state%20governments%20run%20by%20the%20party%20not%20to%20do%20so.%20If%20the%20numbers%20of%20Shudras%20and%20Dwijas%20(Brahmin%2C%20Bania%2C%20Kayastha%2C%20Khatri%20and%20Ksatriyas)%20are%20revealed%2C%20the%20resource%20and%20power-sharing%20will%20have%20to%20be%20done%20on%20that%20basis%20%E2%80%93%20which%20will%20have%20huge%20implications%20for%20the%20Dwija%20control%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20power%20%E2%80%93%20spiritual%20and%20social%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RSS%20historically%20has%20been%20concerned%20about%20maintaining%20Dwija%20control%20of%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20wealth%2C%20power%20and%20also%20the%20Hindu%20spiritual%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20Modi%20government%20buckled%20down%20against%20the%20caste%20count%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20claimed%20OBC%20status%2C%20the%20caste%20discourse%20among%20Shudra%2FOBCs%20has%20been%20scaled%20up.%20The%20critical%20question%20among%20them%20is%20how%20come%20a%20Brahmin%20%E2%80%93%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%93%20is%20calling%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20while%20an%20OBC%20%E2%80%93%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20is%20against%20it.%20The%20RSS%20strategy%20of%20having%20an%20OBC%20PM%20to%20mobilise%20OBC%20voters%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20deep%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhy-the-bjp-is-afraid-of-a-caste-census%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20BJP%20Is%20Afraid%20of%20a%20Caste%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RSS%2C%20which%20never%20accepted%20caste%20as%20a%20category%20of%20electoral%20agenda%2C%20projected%20Modi%20as%20the%20first%20OBC%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20in%202013.%20The%20mainstream%20media%2C%20which%20was%20also%20averse%20to%20a%20discourse%20on%20caste%2C%20carried%20this%20propaganda%20to%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20India.%20Now%20the%20same%20RSS%20and%20media%20are%20opposed%20to%20the%20caste%20census%2C%20whereas%20they%20were%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fews-quota-a-stupefying-inversion-of-the-idea-of-equality%5C%22%3E10%25%20EWS%20reservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20upper%20castes%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-the-issues-to-consider%5C%22%3Ewomen%E2%80%99s%20reservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20without%20an%20OBC%20quota%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20parliament%20and%20in%20assemblies.%20The%20Shudra%2FOBCs%20see%20through%20this%20game%20plan%20of%20the%20RSS%2FBJP%20and%20the%20big%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20at%20all%20the%20RSS%20is%20for%20the%20abolition%20of%20caste%2C%20they%20should%20have%20declared%20an%20agenda%20for%20priesthood%20training%20to%20all%20castes%20by%20abolishing%20the%20Brahmin%20control%20over%20spiritual%20institutions%20like%20temples%2C%20mutts%2C%20gurukuls%20and%20so%20on.%20Another%20equally%20important%20spiritual%20reform%20they%20could%20address%20is%20whether%20Sanskrit%20should%20still%20continue%20as%20the%20language%20of%20prayer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20leave%20that%20aside.%20Why%20do%20they%20not%20take%20the%20initiative%20to%20admit%20boys%20and%20girls%20of%20all%20castes%20for%20priesthood%20training%3F%20Why%20do%20they%20not%20talk%20about%20opening%20up%20schools%20and%20colleges%20for%20Hindu%20theological%20training%2C%20which%20would%20be%20open%20for%20competition%20cutting%20across%20the%20castes%20that%20consider%20themselves%20Hindu%2C%20to%20run%20the%20temples%20and%20other%20spiritual%20institutions%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Gandhian%20agenda%20in%20the%20early%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20did%20not%20go%20that%20far.%20It%20was%20confined%20to%20temple%20entry%20and%20water%20rights%20to%20Shudra%2FOBCs%20and%20Dalits.%20The%20Hindu%20spiritual%20agencies%20agreed%20to%20allow%20Shudra%2FOBCs%20into%20temples%20but%20not%20Dalits%20at%20that%20time.%20However%2C%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20and%20some%20laws%20secured%20temple%20entry%20and%20water%20rights%20to%20Dalits%20to%20a%20large%20extent.%20Why%20is%20the%20RSS%20talking%20about%20these%20old%20issues%20but%20avoiding%20the%20question%20of%20caste%20census%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20big%20media%20houses%20play%20up%20small%20inconsequential%20statements%20by%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20or%20Dattatreya%20Hosabale%20on%20the%20same%20level%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s.%20The%20reason%20is%20that%20the%20RSS%20has%20expanded%20the%20base%20that%20sustains%20the%20Dwija%20control%20of%20all%20systems%20of%20India.%20Now%20they%20think%20that%20the%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Cshown%20their%20place%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%20and%20that%20Shudra%2C%20OBC%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20assertion%20has%20to%20be%20tackled%20with%20tact%20but%20without%20giving%20them%20any%20substantial%20space.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31181250%2FScreenshot-2023-08-31-at-6.12.02-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31181250%2FScreenshot-2023-08-31-at-6.12.02-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31181250%2FScreenshot-2023-08-31-at-6.12.02-PM-300x151.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31181250%2FScreenshot-2023-08-31-at-6.12.02-PM-1024x515.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670898%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22603%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20via%20X%2F%40RahulGandhi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20RSS%20does%20not%20talk%20about%20the%20present%20school%20and%20college%20education%20system%20where%20private%2C%20English%20medium%20schools%20are%20under%20the%20control%20of%20education%20business%20houses.%20The%20government%20school%20and%20college%20education%20in%20regional%20languages%20is%20of%20poor%20quality%20and%20has%20poor%20infrastructure.%20However%2C%20they%20directed%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20stress%20the%20importance%20of%20education%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98mother%20tongue%E2%80%99%20(meaning%20regional%20language)%20in%20the%20government%20sector%20only.%20The%20RSS%20remains%20silent%20about%20providing%20the%20same%20medium%20and%20an%20equal%20standard%20school%20and%20college%20education%20to%20all%20%E2%80%93%20this%20will%20contribute%20to%20the%20eradication%20of%20caste.%20The%20RSS%20leadership%20knows%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENor%20does%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20RSS%20get%20into%20real%20issues%20that%20will%20weaken%20segregation%20based%20on%20caste%20in%20the%20agrarian%20sector.%20Caste%20is%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20the%20graded%20indignity%20of%20labour%20and%20production-related%20science.%20The%20graded%20inequality%20that%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20talked%20about%20was%20institutionalised%20in%20the%20process%20of%20establishing%20graded%20indignity%20of%20labour%20and%20productive%20science.%20For%20example%2C%20leather-related%20scientific%20and%20technological%20work%20is%20treated%20as%20more%20undignified%20than%20tilling%20the%20land%20or%20making%20pots.%20Washing%20clothes%20and%20cutting%20hair%20were%20treated%20as%20more%20undignified%20than%20iron%20and%20gold%20smithy.%20Finally%2C%20temple%20priesthood%20and%20teaching%20in%20gurukuls%20were%20treated%20as%20more%20dignified%20than%20tilling%20the%20land%20and%20harvesting.%20Thus%2C%20the%20temple%20pujari%20and%20gurukul%20teacher%2C%20who%20were%2Fare%20only%20Brahmins%2C%20treated%20all%20other%20tasks%20as%20beneath%20their%20body%20and%20soul.%20The%20RSS%2C%20in%20its%20100%20years%20of%20existence%2C%20never%20tried%20to%20take%20up%20a%20campaign%20against%20these%20indignities%20and%20anti-science%20belief%20systems%20that%20got%20entrenched%20into%20caste%20society%E2%80%99s%20belief%20systems.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20RSS%20is%20serious%20about%20abolishing%20caste%2C%20it%20should%20push%20for%3Cspan%3E%20courses%20about%20the%20dignity%20of%20labour%20and%20respect%20for%20science%20and%20technological%20knowledge%20that%20exists%20in%20tanning%2C%20cutting%20hair%2C%20washing%20clothes%2C%20making%20pots%20and%20tilling%20the%20land%20to%20be%20i%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Entroduced%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUntil%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20no%20political%20leader%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20Brahmim%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20took%20a%20decisive%20stand%20on%20the%20basic%20task%20of%20counting%20castes%20and%20redistributing%20resources%20to%20the%20oppressed.%20Not%20even%20his%20own%20ancestors.%20Among%20upper%20caste%20leaders%2C%20after%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20a%20Bania%2C%20it%20is%20only%20Rahul%20who%20has%20taken%20a%20definite%20stand%20on%20caste.%20One%20has%20to%20wait%20and%20see%20if%20this%20genuine%20commitment%20remains%20in%20the%20future%2C%20but%20his%20stand%20must%20be%20appreciated.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-caste-census-ideological-unity-opposition%5C%22%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20Push%20for%20Caste%20Census%20Is%20a%20Step%20Towards%20Ideological%20Unity%20in%20Opposition%20Ranks%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RSS%2C%20if%20it%20is%20serious%20about%20eradicating%20caste%2C%20should%20start%20a%20campaign%20about%20the%20dignity%20of%20labour%2C%20production%20and%20science%20and%20make%20it%20acceptable%20in%20the%20Hindu%20spiritual%20system.%20The%20course%20content%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges%20must%20have%20teach%20human%20equality%20and%20equal%20respect%20for%20every%20work%20and%20different%20food%20cultures.%20The%20RSS%20must%20ask%20for%20the%20same%20medium%20and%20equal%20quality%20of%20school%20and%20college%20education%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20the%20institute%20is%20government-run%20or%20private.%20Training%20for%20pujaris%20must%20be%20opened%20for%20all%20castes%20that%20claim%20to%20be%20Hindu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership%2C%20which%20mostly%20comprises%20people%20from%20the%20Brahmin%20caste%2C%20has%20the%20will%20for%20such%20a%20reform.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EKancha%20Ilaiah%20Shepherd%20is%20a%20political%20theorist%2C%20social%20activist%20and%20author.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697812240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20161440%2FF06GwWTWcAEgnoO.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fthe-rss-plan-to-eradicate-caste-is-outdated-and-skirts-the-real-issues-of-today%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20it%20is%20serious%2C%20it%20must%20work%20towards%20allowing%20all%20castes%20to%20become%20temple%20priests%20and%20change%20the%20education%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fthe-rss-plan-to-eradicate-caste-is-outdated-and-skirts-the-real-issues-of-today%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Makes%20Dosa%20At%20Roadside%20Eatery%20In%20Poll-Bound%20Telangana%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20Friday%20showed%20off%20his%20culinary%20skills%20by%20making%20dosas%20with%20locals%20at%20a%20roadside%20eatery%20in%20Telangana's%20Jagitial%20district.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20was%20on%20his%20'Vijayabheri%20Yatra'%2C%20a%20foot%20march%20that%20he%20undertook%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20state.%20On%20Friday%2C%20while%20travelling%20to%20Jagtial%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20halted%20at%20the%20Nukapalli%20(NAC)%20bus%20stop%20and%20tried%20his%20culinary%20skills%20by%20making%20the%20South%20Indian%20dish%20at%20a%20roadside%20tiffin%20cart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20Mr%20Gandhi%20making%20dosas%20at%20the%20roadside%20stall.%20In%20the%20clip%2C%20he%20is%20seen%20putting%20the%20dosa%20batter%20on%20a%20hot%20pan%2C%20spreading%20it%20with%20a%20bowl%20and%20flipping%20it%20over.%20Before%20beginning%20the%20process%2C%20he%20is%20also%20seen%20presumably%20asking%20the%20street%20vendor%20about%20the%20process%20of%20making%20the%20dish.%20The%20eatery%20shop%20owner%20and%20others%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20are%20seen%20guiding%20the%20Congress%20leader.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20clip%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20serves%20the%20dosas%20to%20the%20people%2C%20who%20are%20seen%20cheering%20him%20on.%20%26quot%3BRahul%20Anna%2C%26quot%3B%20INC%20wrote%20in%20the%20caption%20of%20the%20post%20along%20with%20a%20heart%20emoji.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20below%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22et%5C%22%3ERahul%20Anna%20%E2%9D%A4%EF%B8%8F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F8bekF4zzjh%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F8bekF4zzjh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Congress%20(%40INCIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1715279541659435513%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20post%2C%20the%20INC%20also%20shared%20a%20series%20of%20pictures%20of%20Mr%20Gandhi%20at%20the%20roadside%20stall.%20%26quot%3BFrom