the%20founders%20of%20Muse%20Wearables%20claim%20that%20it%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cworld%E2%80%99s%20first%20smart%20ring%20to%20offer%20NFC%20payments%20and%20health%20tracking%20in%20the%20smallest%20and%20most%20comfortable%20form%20factor%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20KLN%20Sai%20Prasanth%2C%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Conzumex%20Industries%20%E2%80%94%20which%20operates%20the%20Muse%20Wearables%20brand%20%E2%80%94%20claims%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20there%20are%20health-focused%20rings%20like%20Oura%20in%20the%20USA%20or%20Ultrahuman%2C%20boAt%2C%20etc%20in%20India%2C%20none%20currently%20offer%20the%20combined%20functionality%20of%20NFC%20payments%20and%20health%20tracking%20in%20a%20single%20compact%20ring.%20Also%2C%20most%20rings%20don%E2%80%99t%20offer%20clinical-grade%20accuracy%20for%20monitoring%20most%20vitals%20and%20none%20of%20them%20offer%20cuffless%20BP%20management%20on%20a%20ring%20form%20factor.%20This%20combination%20is%20typically%20found%20in%20smartwatches%20like%20Apple%20Watch%2C%20Galaxy%20Watch%20or%20Garmin%20where%20space%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20constraint.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20sets%20Ring%20One%20apart%20is%20this%20combination%20of%20NFC%20Payments%20and%20advanced%20health%20tracking%20in%20a%20form%20factor%20that%E2%80%99s%20just%203.2%20mm%20thick%20and%207.6%20mm%20wide%20and%20weighs%20less%20than%20five%20grams%2C%20making%20it%20the%20smallest%20and%20most%20comfortable%20wearable%20to%20offer%20this%20convenience%20and%20functionality%20to%20users.%20Moreover%20Ring%20One%20is%20the%20first%20smart%20ring%20in%20the%20world%20to%20offer%20cuffless%20BP%20management%20and%20continuous%20monitoring%20of%20many%20vitals%20with%20clinical%20grade%20accuracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDesigned%20and%20manufactured%20in%20India%2C%20the%20Ring%20One%20has%20already%20entered%20mass%20production.%20And%20to%20facilitate%20that%2C%20Muse%20has%20teamed%20up%20with%20various%20contract%20manufacturers.%20Late%20last%20month%2C%20Muse%20launched%20the%20Ring%20One%20globally.%20In%20India%2C%20however%2C%20the%20product%20is%20set%20for%20launch%20later%20this%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Francis%2C%20CTO%20at%20Muse%20claims%2C%20%E2%80%9CRing%20One%20can%20measure%20six%20di%EF%AC%80erent%20vitals%20%E2%80%94%20heart%20rate%2C%20blood%20oxygen%2C%20temperature%2C%20respiratory%20rate%2C%20heart%20rate%20variability%2C%20and%20blood%20pressure.%20Trained%20with%20five%20million%20data%20points%20from%20over%204%2C000%20people%2C%20Ring%20One%20o%EF%AC%80ers%20clinical%20grade%20accuracy%20for%20health%20information.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRing%20One%20is%20also%20the%20%EF%AC%81rst%20smart%20ring%20in%20the%20world%20to%20o%EF%AC%80er%20cu%EF%AC%80%20less%20blood%20pressure%20measurement.%20It%20detects%20sleep%20and%20naps%2C%20analyses%20various%20sleep%20stages%20and%20gives%20personalised%20insights%20to%20help%20improve%20sleep.%20Ring%20One%20can%20also%20track%20your%20workouts%20and%20give%20you%20advanced%20metrics%20to%20optimise%20your%20%EF%AC%81tness%20gains.%20It%20can%20measure%20the%20impact%20of%20your%20relaxation%20sessions%20and%20helps%20you%20with%20tailored%20insights%20to%20reduce%20your%20stress%20levels%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20recent%20press%20release%20issued%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331198%2Fupcycling-scrap-leather-to-make-luxury-accessories-delhi-fashion-startup-econock%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CRing%20One%20%5Balso%5D%20offers%20the%20convenience%20of%20%E2%80%98tap%20to%20pay%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20a%20simple%20wave%20of%20the%20palm%2C%20Ring%20One%20can%20complete%20transactions%20with%20ease.%20Muse%20has%20partnered%20with%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20payment%20networks%2C%20including%20Mastercard%2C%20VISA%20and%20Rupay%2C%20to%20make%20payments%20with%20the%20Ring%20accessible%20to%20everyone%20across%20the%20world.%20The%20payments%20will%20be%20live%20in%20India%2C%20USA%2C%20Canada%2C%20Europe%2C%20Australia%2C%20Singapore%20and%20UAE%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20press%20release%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202015%20by%20graduates%20from%20IIT%20Madras%20and%20NIT%20Warangal%2C%20Muse%20Wearables%20already%20makes%20payment-enabled%20hybrid%20smartwatches%2C%20health%20trackers%2C%20and%20Gtag%2C%20its%20glucose%20sensor.%20Based%20out%20of%20Bengaluru%20with%20registered%20offices%20in%20Chennai%2C%20USA%2C%20and%20Singapore%2C%20Muse%20currently%20caters%20to%2030%20countries%20by%20selling%20products%20through%20online%20platforms%20to%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse-Wearables-Feature-Image--1697806161.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IIT-M%20Startup%20develops%20Smart%20Ring%20One%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse-Wearables-Feature-Image--1697806161.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse-Wearables-Feature-Image--1697806161-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse-Wearables-Feature-Image--1697806161-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse-Wearables-Feature-Image--1697806161-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse-Wearables-Feature-Image--1697806161-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332711%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Ring%20One%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20Smart%20Ring%20developed%20by%20Indian%20tech%20start-up%20Muse%20Wearables%20is%20equipped%20with%20advanced%20health%20tracking%20%26amp%3B%20NFC%20payments.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20all%20in%20a%20finger%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202018%2C%20we%20launched%20our%20hybrid%20watch%20on%20Kickstarter%20and%20received%20a%20great%20response.%20But%20as%20we%20were%20ready%20to%20scale%20up%20manufacturing%20of%20this%20hybrid%20watch%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298376%2Fmolbio-diagnostics-truenat-covid-testing-raises-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehappened.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20had%20to%20temporarily%20stop%20operations%20and%20realised%20the%20need%20to%20pivot%20quickly%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Prasanth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20onset%20of%20the%20pandemic%20in%20March%202020%20brought%20silent%20hypoxia%20(low%20blood%20oxygen%20levels%20in%20the%20body)%2C%20a%20leading%20cause%20of%20COVID-related%20deaths%2C%20into%20sharp%20focus.%20In%20the%20three-month%20lockdown%20which%20followed%2C%20Prasanth%20and%20his%20team%20were%20immersed%20in%20extensive%20research%20and%20development%20to%20develop%20a%20technology%20that%20could%20accurately%20capture%20low%20blood%20oxygen%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20mission%20was%20to%20engineer%20and%20design%20a%20precise%20sensor%20powered%20by%20leading-edge%20algorithms%20that%20could%20deliver%20nothing%20short%20of%20accurate%20results.%20In%20a%20whirlwind%2090%20days%20from%20design%20to%20production%2C%20we%20launched%20a%20comprehensive%20wrist-based%20health%20tracker%20in%20September%202020%20even%20before%20industry%20leaders%20like%20Apple%20introduced%20wrist%20SpO2%20monitoring%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20there.%20At%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20second%20wave%2C%20we%20deployed%20our%20trackers%20on%20patients%20and%20were%20able%20to%20save%20some%20lives%20by%20generating%20alerts%20to%20provide%20timely%20oxygen%20support.%20We%20learnt%20that%20wearable%20technology%20can%20transform%20lives.%20We%20married%20the%20findings%20from%20our%20past%20two%20products%20and%20came%20up%20with%20the%20path-breaking%20Ring%20One%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Prasanth%20recalls%20a%20personal%20anecdote%20when%20he%20delivered%20Muse%E2%80%99s%20very%20first%20hybrid%20watch%20to%20a%20customer.%20The%20customer%20mentioned%20to%20him%20that%20she%20would%20be%20very%20interested%20to%20see%20such%20features%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmuch%20more%20sleek%20and%20comfortable%20form%20factor%20like%20a%20ring%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20the%20very%20first%20time%20I%20came%20across%20the%20idea%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrathyusha%20K%2C%20co-founder%20and%20COO%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CObserving%20hundreds%20of%20users%20during%20the%20pandemic%20has%20imparted%20us%20with%20priceless%20insights%2C%20most%20notably%20that%20the%20wrist%20might%20not%20be%20the%20most%20optimal%20position%20to%20get%20accurate%20data.%20Also%2C%20many%20people%20were%20unable%20to%20wear%20the%20wrist%20tracker%20during%20sleep.%20We%20found%20that%20the%20%EF%AC%81nger%20is%20a%20more%20accurate%20location%20to%20get%20precise%20data.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Prasanth%2C%20the%20finger%20is%20considered%20a%20more%20accurate%20location%20to%20obtain%20precise%20health%20data.%20Explaining%20his%20reasons%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20because%20the%20finger%20experiences%20less%20interference%20from%20bones%2C%20tendons%20and%20muscles%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20higher%20density%20of%20capillary%20action%2C%20which%20improves%20signal%20quality%20for%20health%20measurements.%20Also%2C%20the%20arteries%20carrying%20blood%20are%20situated%20closer%20to%20the%20finger%20and%20are%20surrounded%20by%20thinner%2C%20more%20uniform%20tissue%20compared%20to%20the%20wrist.%20This%20proximity%20to%20major%20blood%20vessels%20contributes%20to%20more%20accurate%20data.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20rings%20offer%20a%20uniform%20fit%20across%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20people%2C%20unlike%20smartwatches%2C%20which%20can%20vary%20in%20tightness%20and%20positioning%20on%20the%20wrist.%20This%20variation%20can%20affect%20the%20accuracy%20of%20readings.%20This%20is%20why%20doctors%20measure%20heart%20rate%20or%20blood%20oxygen%20from%20the%20finger%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20reasons%20are%20supported%20by%20various%20studies%2C%20such%20as%20one%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7309104%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPubMed%20Central%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20found%20finger-based%20monitoring%20to%20offer%20improved%20signal%20quality.%20Another%20study%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F1424-8220%2F19%2F8%2F1874%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMDPI%20%3C%2Fa%3E(a%20publisher%20of%20open-access%20scientific%20journals)%20highlighted%20the%20advantages%20of%20finger-based%20measurements%20for%20various%20health%20parameters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201500px)%20100vw%2C%201500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FHeropicfinal11-1697806357.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smart%20Ring%20for%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FHeropicfinal11-1697806357.jpg%201500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FHeropicfinal11-1697806357-300x141.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FHeropicfinal11-1697806357-500x235.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FHeropicfinal11-1697806357-768x361.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FHeropicfinal11-1697806357-150x71.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332713%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22706%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Ring%20One%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20Smart%20Ring%20developed%20by%20Indian%20tech%20start-up%20Muse%20Wearables%20can%20measure%20six%20di%EF%AC%80erent%20vitals.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20it%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20advanced%20health%20tracking%2C%20Prasanth%20notes%20that%20Ring%20One%20employs%20LEDs%20that%20project%20light%20into%20your%20arteries%20and%20photo-detectors%20that%20capture%20the%20reflected%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20photo-detectors%20come%20with%20lenses%20with%20optimised%20curvature%20to%20enhance%20the%20light%20collected%20and%20ensure%20great%20signal%20quality.%20The%20properties%20of%20the%20reflected%20light%20change%20based%20on%20your%20blood%20flow.%20These%20changes%20are%20captured%20in%20the%20signal%20received%20by%20the%20photo-detectors.%20Ring%20One%20uses%20a%20total%20of%20six%20LEDs%20(green%2C%20red%20and%20IR)%20and%20two%20photo-detectors%20to%20give%20you%20accurate%20readings%20all%20through%20the%20day.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Ring%20One%20also%20captures%20your%20movement%20in%20six%20different%20axes%20using%20the%203D%20accelerometer%20and%20gyroscope.%20This%20ensures%20that%20you%20get%20accurate%20health%20vital%20measurements%20even%20when%20you%20are%20working%20out%20or%20are%20on%20the%20move%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20simple%20terms%2C%20Ring%20One%20observes%20your%20blood%20flow%20patterns%20using%20an%20optical%20sensor%20to%20track%20all%20your%20vitals%20like%20respiratory%20rate%2C%20SPO2%20and%20BP%2C%20amongst%20others.%20It%20also%20uses%20a%20temperature%20sensor%20to%20measure%20your%20temperature%20changes%20all%20through%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20contactless%20payments%2C%20the%20user%20can%20enter%20their%20card%20details%20on%20the%20Muse%20app.%20These%20details%20are%20encrypted%20and%20sent%20securely%20to%20their%20ring%E2%80%99s%20NFC%20chip.%20They%20can%20then%20tap%20the%20Ring%20across%20any%20PoS%20(point%20of%20sale)%20terminal%20to%20make%20a%20payment%20similar%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctap%20to%20pay%E2%80%9D%20payment%20done%20with%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20users%20can%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20the%20Ring%20One%20with%20minimal%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F265807%2Feducation-campaign-help-students-villages-study-smartphones-during-lockdown%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmartphone%20%3C%2Fa%3Eintervention%2C%20Muse%20has%20designed%20two%20key%20interfaces%20%E2%80%94%20Turn%20Wheel%20and%20Magic%20Glyph.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Turn%20Wheel%2C%20users%20can%20switch%20between%20different%20modes.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20simple%20turn%20to%20the%20left%20can%20start%20a%20workout%20mode%20and%20monitor%20their%20health%20while%20exercising%20without%20needing%20their%20phone.%20Likewise%2C%20users%20can%20enable%20payments%20with%20a%20quick%20turn%20to%20the%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20like%20having%20a%20convenient%20and%20intuitive%20controller%20on%20your%20ring.%20It%20also%20helps%20add%20additional%20layers%20of%20security%20to%20your%20payments.%20You%20can%20use%20the%20turn%20wheel%20interface%20to%20lock%20the%20payments%20and%20enable%20them%20only%20when%20you%20want%20to%20ensure%20no%20phishing%20can%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prasanth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Magic%20Glyph%20interface%20is%20all%20about%20showing%20users%20the%20most%20important%20information%20at%20a%20glance.%20It%20lets%20them%20check%20things%20like%20the%20charging%20levels%20of%20the%20ring%20and%20case.%20Also%2C%20if%20a%20user%20ever%20misplaces%20their%20ring%20or%20case%2C%20they%20can%20use%20the%20Magic%20Glyph%20interface%20to%20locate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMade%20with%20Titanium%20grade%202%20and%20Ceramic%20(Zirconia)%2C%20this%20smart%20ring%20is%20lightweight%20yet%20robust.%20Going%20further%2C%20the%20inner%20layer%20of%20the%20ring%20is%20made%20with%20medical-grade%20epoxy%20to%20ensure%20users%20have%20a%20certain%20degree%20of%20comfort%20during%20wear.%20Also%2C%20the%20Ring%20One%20is%20water%20resistant%20up%20to%20100%20metres.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse--1697806481.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smart%20Ring%20Innovation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse--1697806481.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse--1697806481-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse--1697806481-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse--1697806481-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse--1697806481-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332715%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Representational%20I