uploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20171219%2FF8N0WYHWsAAL58Q.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20171219%2FF8N0WYHWsAAL58Q-300x182.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20171219%2FF8N0WYHWsAAL58Q-1024x622.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681076%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22729%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20the%20holy%20Parvati%20Kund%20of%20Pithoragarh%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20Photo%3A%20X%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20akin%20to%20the%20garb%20he%20chose%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20first%20COVID-19%20lockdown.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20growing%20locks%20and%20flowing%20beard%20made%20him%20look%20sagely%20and%20saved%20him%20for%20being%20pinioned%20for%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20shortfalls%20and%20lack%20of%20foresight.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20visit%20to%20Uttarakhand%2C%20he%20performed%20and%20enacted%20multiple%20roles%2C%20even%20when%20addressing%20a%20public%20meeting.%20The%20ostensible%20occasion%20was%20the%20inauguration%20and%20foundation-laying%20ceremony%20of%20multiple%20projects%20in%20Pithoragarh%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20most%20publicised%20picture(s)%20were%20those%20in%20a%20creamy%20shade%20of%20white%20underscoring%20the%20%E2%80%98purity%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20person%20donning%20the%20costume.%20Modi%20went%20to%20the%20Shiva%20temple%20located%20at%20a%20dizzying%20height%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Parvati%20Kund%20wearing%20this%20costume.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20exotic%20locales%20have%20their%20own%20appeal.%20But%20in%20this%20case%2C%20as%20indicated%20in%20Bachchan%E2%80%99s%20post%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20spot%20where%20numerous%20devout%20Hindus%20aspire%20to%20go%20and%20pay%20obeisance%20to%20Lord%20Shiva.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20such%20settings%20enable%20Modi%20to%20display%20himself%20as%20a%20leader%20who%20is%20also%20a%20saviour%20of%20people.%20With%20this%20act%20particularly%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20conveyed%20to%20people%20that%20to%20seek%20boons%20and%20blessings%20for%20them%20he%20even%20%E2%80%98undertakes%20the%20hardship%E2%80%99%20of%20trekking%20up%20to%20such%20remote%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20posts%20buttresses%20this%20point%3A%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20this%20place%20of%20spirituality%20and%20culture%20situated%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20nature%2C%20I%20wished%20a%20happy%20life%20for%20all%20the%20family%20members%20of%20our%20country.%E2%80%9D%20The%20message%20was%20unambiguous%20%E2%80%93%20he%20has%20travelled%20this%20far%2C%20not%20to%20partake%20in%20the%20visual%20wonderment%20that%20the%20images%20arouse%2C%20or%20tick%20another%20destination%20from%20his%20%E2%80%98to-visit%E2%80%99%20list%2C%20but%20to%20seek%20well-being%20of%20%E2%80%98his%20people%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20posts%20depicted%20the%20premier%20in%20the%20designer%20costume%20(obviously)%20worn%20over%20layers%20of%20woolens%20with%20a%20headgear%20in%20place.%20A%20search%20revealed%20that%20the%20outfit%20Modi%20wore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Farchive%2Ffeatures%2Frang-tribals-from-pithoragarh-nepal-come-together-287798%5C%22%3Eis%20actually%20donned%20by%20men%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20particular%20tribal%20community%20of%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20inside%20the%20cave%20in%20the%20Kedarnath%20temple%20complex%20in%20May%202019%2C%20where%20his%20videos%20and%20pictures%20drew%20sniggers%20from%20critics%20due%20to%20%E2%80%98access%E2%80%99%20provided%20to%20the%20unidentified%20cameraperson(s)%2C%20at%20this%20Pithoragarh%20shrine%2C%20too%2C%20the%20intrusive%20presence%20of%20the%20camera%20did%20not%20alter%20the%20tranquil%20expression%20he%20sported%20on%20his%20face%20throughout%20while%20performing%20rituals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20served%20as%20a%20reminder%20to%20an%20old%20aide%E2%80%99s%20observation%20made%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%3A%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20square%20inch%20outside%20his%20private%20room%20is%20a%20stage%2C%E2%80%9D%20quite%20like%20makeshift%20ones%20in%20his%20school%20in%20Vadnagar%2C%20which%20he%20went%20to.%20One%20of%20his%20teachers%20had%20provided%20a%20detail%3A%20He%20accepted%20only%20lead%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPresentation%20of%20the%20self%20has%20been%20increasingly%20central%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20politics.%20An%20early%20user%20of%20social%20media%2C%20he%20became%20aware%20of%20how%20technology%20could%20enhance%20appeal%20of%20the%20aesthete.%20Through%20the%20power%20of%20his%20oratory%2C%20he%20conveys%20repeatedly%20that%20none%20of%20this%20is%20for%20himself%2C%20but%20only%20%E2%80%98for%E2%80%99%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20engagements%20for%20that%20day%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20how%20the%20religious%20or%20spiritual%20conjoined%20with%20the%20cultural%20and%20political.%20This%20was%20understandable%20because%20the%20amalgamation%20of%20the%20three%20is%20one%20of%20the%20foundational%20tenets%20of%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20culture%2C%20religion%2C%20and%20nationalism%20are%20interwoven%20and%20universal%20to%20the%20Indian%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20course%20of%20the%20day%2C%20Modi%20traipsed%20past%20assemblies%20of%20personnel%20of%20the%20Army%2C%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%20and%20Indo%20Tibetan%20Border%20Police%20besides%20the%20%3Cem%3Eaam%20janta%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20many%20of%20who%20were%20assembled%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20route%20he%20took%2C%20with%20a%20mandate%20to%20cheer%20and%20shower%20floral%20petals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPast%20these%20halts%2C%20Modi%20hopped%20off%20to%20another%20ancient%20Shiva%20temple%20in%20Jageshwar%20Dham%20in%20Almora%20district.%20In%20between%20he%20had%20time%20to%20address%20a%20public%20rally%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20never%20fails%20to%20wear%20his%20religiosity%20on%20his%20sleeves%20overtly%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20on%20this%20day%20or%20in%20May%202019%20in%20Kedarnath%2C%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20or%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2792xwvS7yg%26ab_channel%3DSansadTV%5C%22%3EAyodhya%20in%20December%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUTfKUQ-7P_A%5C%22%3EAugust%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThrough%20these%20acts%2C%20Modi%20projects%20himself%20not-so-subtly%20as%20a%20devout%20Hindu.%20However%20he%20remains%20a%20utopian%20figure%2C%20whose%20%E2%80%98perfection%E2%80%99%20is%20impractical%20for%20hoi%20polloi.%20Modi%20can%20at%20best%20be%20an%20aspiration%2C%20never%20fulfilled%20for%20no%20one%20can%20become%20or%20take%20his%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20he%20and%20his%20party%20publicised%20his%20OBC%20status%20but%20not%20anymore.%20Whenever%20he%20speaks%20on%20anything%20that%20has%20a%20resonance%20of%20the%20Hindu%2C%20Hinduism%20and%20Hinduness%20(Savarkar%20called%20this%20the%20near%20closest%20word%20to%20define%20Hindutva)%2C%20he%20blurs%20caste%2C%20class%20and%20regional%20lines%20%E2%80%93%20he%20is%20just%20a%20Hindu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20separation%20between%20religion%20and%20state.%20Effectively%2C%20the%20latter%20has%20actually%20acquired%20a%20far%20deeper%20religious%20hue%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20every%20playacting%20of%20Modi%20is%20within%20a%20temple%20or%20religious%20precincts.%20On%20October%201%2C%20TV%20screens%20and%20social%20media%20platforms%20lit%20up%20with%20Modi%20with%20a%20broom.%20He%20did%20so%20not%20all%20by%20himself%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fbroom-in-hand-modi-collaborates-with-influencer-for-swachh-drive%2Farticleshow%2F104092240.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Echose%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20prop%20in%20the%20singular%20%E2%80%93%20Ankit%20Baiyanpuria%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20new%20tribe%20of%20%E2%80%98influencers%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20field%20of%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20marked%20the%20second%20fortnight%20of%20September%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fswachhbharatmission.gov.in%2Fshs2023%2FSHS2023%2Findex.aspx%5C%22%3ESwachhata%20Hi%20Seva%3C%2Fa%3E%20(like%20most%20official%20programmes%2C%20the%20naming%20of%20this%20too%20was%20solely%20in%20Hindi).%20The%20campaign%20was%20to%20end%20on%20October%202%20%E2%80%93%20a%20day%20when%20the%20mandatory%20visit%20to%20Rajghat%20hogs%20time%20and%20space%20in%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20video%20clip%20was%20smartly%20released%20a%20day%20prior%20to%20this.%20Almost%20from%20the%20first%20shot%2C%20it%20is%20understandable%20that%20the%20production%20team%20was%20briefed%20that%20Modi%20was%20the%20star.%20The%20spotlight%20remained%20riveted%20on%20his%20face%2C%20while%20the%20%E2%80%98co-star%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20was%20often%20shrouded%20in%20darkness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20two%2C%20while%20Modi%20was%20dressed%20in%20kurta%20pyjamas%20with%20a%20white%20wrap%20as%20an%20accessory%2C%20draped%20or%20pinned%20strategically%20over%20his%20shoulder%2C%20Baiyanpuria%20was%20in%20a%20normal%20workout%20costume%20%E2%80%93%20tracksuit%20bottom%20and%20a%20round-neck%20T-shirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20projects%20Modi%20as%20a%20leader%20who%20is%20also%20concerned%20about%20cleanliness%20or%20Swachhata%20and%20fitness%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20all%20about%20that%20Swachh%20and%20Swasth%20Bharat%20vibe%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20post%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShot%20in%20an%20open%20space%20with%20large%20trees%20providing%20the%20backdrop%20to%20simulate%20a%20park%2C%20shooting%20may%20even%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20backyard%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20intention%20is%20to%20publicise%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Mission%20by%20personally%20picking%20up%20the%20broom.%20The%20two%20characters%20banter%20along%20%E2%80%93%20the%20contents%20aimed%20at%20furthering%20Modi-centric%20mythologies%20%E2%80%93%20Baiyanpuria%20says%20that%20he%20drew%20inspiration%20from%20Modi%20for%20his%20fitness%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20again%20the%20unattainable%20Modi%20who%20is%20the%20star%20of%20this%20widely%20viewed%20video.%20This%20social%20media%20influencer%20from%20Sonipat%20may%20have%204.9%20millions%20followers%20on%20Instagram%2C%20but%20all%20efforts%20would%20have%20come%20to%20a%20naught%20had%20he%20not%20been%20inspired%20by%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20becomes%20part%20of%20the%20people%20by%20articulating%20their%20sentiments%20and%20desires.%20He%20is%20part%20of%20the%20elite%20that%20people%20aspire%20to%20become%20part%20of%20with%20his%20style%20of%20dressing%20and%20through%20the%20raw%20political%20power%20he%20exudes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20has%20always%20been%20aware%20of%20the%20power%20of%20how%20the%20leader%20is%20%E2%80%98presented%E2%80%99.%20He%20is%20not%20the%20only%20one%20in%20the%20world%20for%20whom%20the%20template%20of%20a%20populist%20is%20apt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhere%20he%20scores%20over%20his%20peers%20is%20the%20additional%20flank%20of%20religion%20through%20which%20he%20makes%20inroads%20and%20creates%20a%20following%20for%20himself%20in%20the%20psyche%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20constant%20use%20of%20religion%20and%20the%20religious%20vocabulary%2C%20there%20is%20a%20perceived%20messianic%20zeal%20in%20his%20actions.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20recollect%20that%20on%20more%20than%20one%20occasion%2C%20Modi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Fin-depth%2Felections-2014-narendra-modi-takes-charge%2Fstory%2Fi-have-been-chosen-by-god-says-narendra-modi-46973-2014-04-24%5C%22%3Ehas%20claimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20has%20been