t%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emake%20Israeli%20voices%20%E2%80%9Cespecially%20visible%20at%20the%20fair%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0they%20are%20closing%20out%20the%20space%20for%20a%20Palestinian%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Shibli%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ci%3EMinor%20Detail%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0has%20been%20smeared%20as%20being%20anti-Semitic%20by%20two%20journalists%20and%20literary%20editors%2C%20other%20serious%20literary%20critics%20have%20clearly%20refuted%20this%20in%20the%20German%20press%20and%20elsewhere.%20The%20book%20makes%20reference%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2F2003-10-29%2Fty-article%2Fi-saw-fit-to-remove-her-from-the-world%2F0000017f-db62-d856-a37f-ffe2fa5b0000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewell-documented%20events%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0related%20to%20the%20rape%20of%20a%20Bedouin%20girl%20in%201949%20by%20an%20Israeli%20army%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShibli%E2%80%99s%20UK%20publisher%2C%20Jacques%20Testard%20of%20Fitzcarraldo%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20purposes%20of%20literature%20is%20to%20encourage%20understanding%20and%20dialogue%20between%20cultures.%20At%20a%20time%20of%20such%20horrific%20violence%20and%20heartbreak%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20book%20fair%20has%20a%20duty%20to%20champion%20literary%20voices%20from%20Palestine%20and%20Israel.%20We%20stand%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Adania%20Shibli%20and%20her%20German%20publishers%2C%20Berenberg%20Verlag.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20spirit%2C%20those%20of%20us%20involved%20in%20writing%2C%20translation%2C%20and%20publishing%20strongly%20assert%20that%20canceling%20cultural%20events%20is%20not%20the%20way%20forward.%20We%20recall%20the%20Frankfurt%20book%20fair%20supporting%20Turkish%20publishers%2C%20and%20how%20last%20year%20Ukrainian%20president%20Zelensky%20spoke%20to%20the%20fair%20in%20a%20pre-recorded%20address.%C2%A0The%20Frankfurt%20Book%20Fair%20has%20a%20responsibility%2C%20as%20a%20major%20international%20book%20fair%2C%20to%20be%20creating%20spaces%20for%20Palestinian%20writers%20to%20share%20their%20thoughts%2C%20feelings%2C%20reflections%20on%20literature%20through%20these%20terrible%2C%20cruel%20times%2C%20not%20shutting%20them%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20look%20for%20new%20language%20and%20new%20ideas%20in%20order%20to%20approach%20these%20bleak%20times%20in%20a%20new%20way.%20For%20this%2C%20we%20need%20writers%20%E2%80%93%20including%20Palestinian%20writers%20%E2%80%93%20more%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697807736000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19123630%2FF8exa0MXQAAjnaV.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fover-1300-writers-publishers-decry-cancellation-of-events-featuring-palestinian-authors-artists%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20letter%20of%20support%2C%20signed%20by%20several%20Nobel%20laureates%20and%20Booker%20Prize%20winners%2C%20condemned%20the%20cancellation%20of%20events%20featuring%20Palestinian%20art%2C%20voices%2C%20and%20stories%20across%20Europe%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fover-1300-writers-publishers-decry-cancellation-of-events-featuring-palestinian-authors-artists%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aamir%20Khan%20to%20relocate%20to%20Chennai%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697807622000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104587528%2Cimgsize-32276.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fis-aamir-khan-planning-to-relocate-to-chennai-from-mumbai-heres-what-we-know-%2Farticleshow%2F104587528.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%2