ink%20in%20the%20plastic%20recycling%20chain%2C%20and%20also%20the%20ones%20facing%20the%20most%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERunning%20nearly%20entirely%20as%20an%20informal%20economy%2C%20aardhis%20have%20the%20skill%20and%20eye%20to%20sort%20the%20waste%20without%20any%20chemical%20testing%20or%20lab%20equipment.%20All%20they%20need%20is%20empty%20stretches%20of%20land.%20However%2C%20they%20are%20constantly%20caught%20in%20a%20cat-and-mouse%20chase%20with%20the%20authorities.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20we%20were%20removed%20from%20Mundka%2C%20then%20from%20Kamruddin%20Nagar%20and%20they%20are%20still%20chasing%20us%20away%20even%20after%20we%E2%80%99ve%20crossed%20the%20Delhi%20border%E2%80%9D%20said%2038-year-old%20Rajesh%2C%20an%20aardhi%20at%20the%20Shiddipur%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajesh%20and%20Bablu%20weren%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20%3Cem%3Eaardhis%3C%2Fem%3E%20angry%20with%20the%20government.%20The%20huddle%20of%20two%20gradually%20swelled%20to%20about%2015%20men%20and%20a%20few%20women%20all%20expressing%20their%20frustration%20at%20the%20treatment%20they%20receive%20from%20the%20municipal%20corporation%20and%20national%20green%20tribunal%20officials.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20come%20and%20raze%20our%20temporary%20structures%20whenever%20they%20feel%20like%20it.%20I%20want%20to%20quit%20this%20profession%20now.%20If%20the%20government%20worked%20as%20hard%20as%20the%20waste%20pickers%2C%20the%20country%20would%20be%20elsewhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%2055-year-old%20Mangeram%2C%20who%20lost%20most%20of%20his%20business%20when%20he%20left%20the%20market%20at%20Mundka.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAardhis%20believe%20that%20they%20are%20not%20the%20problem%2C%20but%20a%20solution%20to%20a%20problem.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20plastic%20is%20not%20going%20to%20decompose%20itself.%20If%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20clean%20this%20mess%20then%20there%20will%20be%20heaps%20lying%20around%20in%20the%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%2025-year-old%20Sonu%2C%20who%20works%20with%20his%20father%20at%20the%20market%20in%20Lowa.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20aardhis%20told%20me%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20waste%20that%20makes%20it%20way%20to%20these%20plastic%20markets.%20The%20government%20imports%20plastic%20waste%2C%20charges%20a%20custom%20duty%20on%20it%20and%20then%20the%20dealers%20pay%20an%2018%25%20GST%20on%20subsequent%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20is%20trying%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20bigger%20factories%20contributing%20to%20pollution%20in%20broad%20daylight%20because%20their%20owners%20can%20pay%20off%20the%20officials.%20We%20are%20preventing%20pollution%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20but%20nobody%20cares%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%2036-year-old%20aardhi%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20named%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20traders%20work%20under%20the%20scorching%20sun%20without%20access%20to%20toilets%20or%20a%20clean%20resting%20place%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20refuge%20away%20from%20the%20piles%20of%20waste.%20While%20they%20pride%20themselves%20on%20keeping%20Delhi%20%E2%80%9Cfrom%20coming%20to%20a%20standstill%2C%20trapped%20under%20its%20own%20garbage%E2%80%9D%2C%20most%20of%20them%20seem%20to%20have%20lost%20hope%20and%20plan%20to%20move%20back%20to%20their%20villages%20if%20they%20face%20further%20harassment%20by%20government%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20ironic%20that%20their%20contribution%20to%20waste%20management%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20guarantee%20them%20any%20financial%20or%20personal%20security.%20To%20quote%20Kaveri%20Gill%2C%20the%20author%20%3Cem%3EOf%20Plastic%20and%20Poverty%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20few%20to%20document%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20informal%20recycling%20markets%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20them%2C%20leave%20them%20alone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeveloped%20in%20collaboration%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fekaansh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5