20Oregon.%20Rather%20than%20wheels%2C%20Digit%20walks%20on%20two%20legs.%20It%20is%205%20feet%209%20inches%20tall%20and%20weighs%2065%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20robot%20can%20walk%20backwards%2C%20forwards%20and%20sideways%2C%20and%20can%20even%20crouch.%20It%20has%20arms%20that%20can%20pick%20up%20and%20move%20packages%2C%20containers%2C%20customer%20orders%20and%20objects.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20initial%20use%20for%20this%20technology%20will%20be%20to%20help%20employees%20with%20tote%20recycling%2C%20a%20highly%20repetitive%20process%20of%20picking%20up%20and%20moving%20empty%20totes%20once%20inventory%20has%20been%20completely%20picked%20out%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Amazon%20said%20in%20a%20blog%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697804820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F0bjm0dtg_amazon-robot-warehouse-1200_625x300_20_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-launches-humanoid-robots-at-warehouses-denies-fears-of-employee-displacement-4500164%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20robot%20can%20walk%20backwards%2C%20forwards%20and%20sideways%2C%20and%20can%20even%20crouch.%20It%20has%20arms%20that%20can%20pick%20up%20and%20move%20packages%2C%20containers%2C%20customer%20orders%20and%20objects.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-launches-humanoid-robots-at-warehouses-denies-fears-of-employee-displacement-4500164%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-launches-humanoid-robots-at-warehouses-denies-fears-of-employee-displacement-4500164%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-launches-humanoid-robots-at-warehouses-denies-fears-of-employee-displacement-4500164%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CDS's%20Undiplomatic%20Talk%20of%20Russian%20'Decline'%20Turns%20Focus%20