rts%20have%20carried%20images%20of%20Palestinian%20suffering%2C%20with%20some%20prominently%20citing%20Palestinian%20sources%20as%20saying%20Israel%20was%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNone%20of%20the%20reality%20that%20shocked%20much%20of%20the%20world%20on%20October%207%20is%20in%20Chinese%20news.%20Instead%2C%20the%20news%20features%20Israeli%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20without%20explaining%20that%20the%20target%20is%20only%20Hamas%20infrastructure%2C%26quot%3B%20Carice%20Witte%2C%20director%20of%20the%20SIGNAL%20Group%2C%20a%20Sino-Israel%20relations%20think%20tank%20based%20in%20Tel%20Aviv.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeeking%20Allies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20gives%20it%20an%20added%20incentive%20to%20align%20itself%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20been%20trying%2C%20with%20limited%20success%2C%20to%20persuade%20the%20global%20south%20to%20rally%20behind%20Ukraine.%20Portraying%20the%20US%20as%20a%20driver%20of%20the%20conflict%20helps%20blunt%20that%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlterman%20sees%20a%20similar%20motivation%20for%20China%2C%20which%20regards%20the%20U.S.%20as%20its%20chief%20geopolitical%20rival.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20is%20trying%20to%20play%20the%20global%20south%20card%2C%20irrespective%20of%20its%20close%20ties%20to%20Israel.%20More%20than%20actually%20supporting%20Hamas%2C%20it%20is%20quietly%20helping%20build%20resistance%20to%20US%20efforts%20to%20build%20international%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alterman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMa%20Xiaolin%2C%20a%20Middle%20East%20expert%20and%20professor%20at%20Zhejiang%20International%20Studies%20University%2C%20said%20China%20was%20being%20even-handed%20between%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20Israel%20but%20if%20pushed%2C%20would%20side%20with%20its%20Arab%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Israel%2C%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20expa