20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emarjara%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evrata%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20There%20was%20talk%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Vaishnava%20bhakti%20or%20devotion%2C%20about%20different%20ways%20through%20which%20a%20devotee%20approaches%20his%20ishta%20deity.%20There%20are%20many%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enyayas%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Emethods%20or%20theories%20%E2%80%93%20but%20the%20two%20most%20often%20cited%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emarkata%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enyaya%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emarjara%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enyaya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20former%20refers%20to%20how%20the%20young%20one%20of%20a%20monkey%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emarkata%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20Sanskrit%20%E2%80%93%20approaches%20God%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20to%20how%20the%20young%20one%20of%20a%20cat%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emarjara%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Edoes.%20Briefly%20put%2C%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emarkata-nyaya%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Erefers%20to%20the%20behaviour%20of%20a%20baby%20monkey%2C%20who%20clings%20tightly%20to%20its%20mother%20wherever%20she%20goes.%20The%20mother%20monkey%E2%80%99s%20arms%20are%20occupied%20as%20she%20leaps%20from%20tree%20to%20tree%3B%20she%20does%20not%20hold%20on%20to%20the%20baby%3B%20but%20as%20long%20as%20the%20baby%20holds%20firmly%20to%20her%2C%20it%20arrives%20safely%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhereas%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emarjara-nyaya%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Erefers%20to%20the%20behaviour%20of%20kittens%2C%20who%20are%20likely%20to%20wander.%20The%20mother%20cat%20picks%20them%20up%20by%20the%20scruff%20of%20the%20neck%20and%20carries%20them%20wherever%20she%20wants%20them%20to%20be.%20The%20kitten%20is%20passive%3B%20she%20makes%20no%20effort%20but%20arrives%20safely%20by%20surrendering%20to%20the%20mother%E2%80%99s%20protective%20grasp.%E2%80%99%20It%20is%20up%20to%20the%20devotee%2C%20then%2C%20to%20choose%3A%20to%20keep%20making%20an%20effort%20to%20cling%20for%20succour%20to%20his%20deity%2C%20or%20to%20leave%20everything%20to%20the%20deity%2C%20trusting%20him%20and%20surrendering%20to%20him%20completely.%20No%20recommendation%20is%20made%2C%20no%20preference%20indicated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20368px)%2085vw%2C%20368px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20145724%2FScreenshot-2023-10-20-at-2.55.30.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22368%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20145724%2FScreenshot-2023-10-20-at-2.55.30.png%20958w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20145724%2FScreenshot-2023-10-20-at-2.55.30-240x300.png%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20145724%2FScreenshot-2023-10-20-at-2.55.30-817x1024.png%20817w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681033%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22461%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPRINCESS%20WATCHING%20A%20MAID%20KILLING%20A%20SNAKE%2C%20By%20Mir%20Kalan%20Khan%2C%20Lucknow%3B%20c.%201770%2C%20%5BCollection%3A%20British%20Library%3B%20Johnson%20Album%2015%2C%20no.%208%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3ENever%20having%20heard%20of%20any%20of%20this%20before%2C%20I%20was%20fascinated.%20But%20even%20more%20fascinating%20for%20me%20was%20the%20use%20of%20the%20term%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emarjara-vrata.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20common%20usage%20it%20stands%20simply%20for%20%E2%80%98a%20cat-like%20observance%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20the%20term%20is%20not%20neutral.%20It%20really%20has%20come%20to%20stand%20for%20%E2%80%98concealing%20one%E2%80%99s%20malice%20or%20evil%20designs%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20piety%20or%20virtue%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20an%20accusation%20that%20one%20person%20might%20fling%20at%20his%20rival%20while%20calling%20him%20a%20%E2%80%98cheat%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20a%20%E2%80%98hypocrite%E2%80%99.%20In%20an%20episode%20in%20that%20ancient%20epic%20of%20ours%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMahabharata%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Duryodhana%20charges%20even%20the%20noble%20Yudhishthira%20with%20observing%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emarjara-vrata%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20not%20once%2C%20but%20repeatedly.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClearly%2C%20the%20cat%20had%20come%20to%20stand%20for%20%E2%80%98hypocrisy%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98ye%20gods%2C%20that%20person%20whose%20standard%20of%20righteousness%20is%20always%20up%2C%20but%20whose%20sins%20are%20always%20concealed%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20opprobrium%20seems%20to%20have%20endured%20over%20a%20very%20long%20time%3A%20cleverness%2C%20hypocrisy%2C%20avarice%2C%20inscrutability%2C%20thievery.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%20enough%2C%20however%2C%20in%20our%20land%20at%20the%20same%20time%20there%20is%20no%20real%20dislike%20for%20cats.%20There%20are%20superstitions%20around%20her%20figure%2C%20for%20certain%2C%20and%20stories%20go%20on%20being%20repeated.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20no%20fatwas%20have%20been%20passed%3B%20no%20papal%20bulls%20issued.%20Great%20poets%20like%20Mir%20and%20Ghalib%20loved%20their%20cats%20to%20distraction%3B%20the%20poet%20Jibanananda%20Das%20saw%20himself%20in%20a%20cat%20that%20went%20here%20and%20there%2C%20following%20the%20Sun%3B%20Vikram%20Seth%20saw%20her%20as%20full%20of%20mischief%20and%20cleverness%20but%20no%20evil.%20In%20fact%2C%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20the%20feline%20is%20%E2%80%98addressed%E2%80%99%20almost%20with%20affection.%20She%20is%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emaano%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emaaoon%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emausi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(mother%E2%80%99s%20sister)%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Episshi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ebiloongari%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20if%20one%20goes%20by%20usage%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20northern%20parts%20of%20our%20land.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20somewhere%20out%20of%20these%20memories%20and%20stray%20thoughts%20and%20scattered%20observations%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%20was%20mock-admonishment%20that%20I%20received%20as%20an%20art%20historian%2C%20seductive%20and%20long-buried%20snippets%20that%20reading%20about%20cats%20yielded%2C%20or%20the%20fact%20that%20my%20son%20adopted%20recently%20two%20cats%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20present%20work%20has%20emerged.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20reader%20is%20entitled%20to%20ask%3A%20%E2%80%98So%3F%E2%80%99%20But%20he%20will%20at%20least%20find%20inside%20absorbing%20tales%20and%20images%20and%20poetry%20and%20proverbs%2C%20that%20I%20gathered%20together.%20All%20on%20cats.%20Indian%20cats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20word%20of%20explanation%20to%20end%20with%2C%20however.%20Inadvertently%2C%20because%20one%20is%20so%20used%20to%20it%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20life%2C%20the%20cat%20in%20my%20account%20is%20always%20taken%20to%20be%20a%20female.%20Lacking%20in%20logic%20as%20this%20is%2C%20the%20gender%20is%20open%20to%20change.%20Second%20word%3A%20the%20book%20is%20confined%2C%20strictly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Econfined%2C%20to%20cats%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20domestic%20cats%20%E2%80%93%20not%20because%20they%20are%20unique%2C%20but%20because%20cats%20elsewhere%20%E2%80%93%20and%20they%20are%20everywhere%20%E2%80%93%20have%20their%20own%20histories%2C%20their%20own%20tales%2C%20their%20own%20place%20in%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EB.N.%20Goswamy%20is%20an%20Indian%20art%20critic%2C%20art%20historian%20and%20a%20former%20vice%20chairman%20of%20the%20Sarabhai%20Foundation%20of%20Ahmedabad%2C%20which%20runs%20the%20Calico%20Museum%20of%20Textiles.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20images%20are%20from%20the%20book%20and%20have%20been%20reproduced%20with%20permission.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697798758000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20142823%2F2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fart-history-cats-bn-goswamy-indian-cat%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20well%20known%20art%20historian%20writes%20a%20delightful%20and%20whimsical%20%E2%80%93%20and%20well%20researched%20treatise%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20world%20of%20cats.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fart-history-cats-bn-goswamy-indian-cat%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ousted%20president's%20escape%20attempt%20thwarted%2C%20Niger%20junta%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697797440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-niger-mohamed-bazoum_6328133.jpg%3F20231020120353%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fousted-presidents-escape-attempt-thwarted-niger-junta-says-12988283%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Niger's%20ruling%20military%20junta%20has%20said%20it%20thwarted%20an%20overnight%20attempt%20by%20deposed%20President%20Mohamed%20Bazoum%20to%20escape%20detention.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fousted-presidents-escape-attempt-thwarted-niger-junta-says-12988283%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fousted-presidents-escape-attempt-thwarted-niger-junta-says-12988283%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fousted-presidents-escape-attempt-thwarted-niger-junta-says-12988283%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22For%20the%20First%20Time%20in%20Eight%20Years%2C%20PM%20Gram%20Sadak%20Yojana%20Achieves%20Q1%20Target%20in%20FY24%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F14113428%2FToll_Plaza_on_Roads_in_India_NH_27_National_Highway_Rajasthan_NH76_old_system_in_India.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Gram%20Sadak%20Yojana%20(PMGSY)%20has%20exceeded%20its%20target%20for%20rural%20road%20construction%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year%2C%20with%206%2C403%20kilometres%20of%20roads%20constructed%20against%20a%20target%20of%206%2C000%20km%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Frural-road-construction-sees-turnaround-for-the-first-time-in-8-years-nso-123101900924_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20cited%20the%20National%20Statistical%20Office%20(NSO)%20in%20its%20latest%20Twenty%20Point%20Programme%20(TPP)%20progress%20report%20for%20the%20April-June%20quarter%20of%20FY24.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20eight%20years%20that%20the%20scheme%20has%20achieved%20its%20first-quarter%20target.%20It%20has%20been%20under-performing%20in%20recent%20years.%20The%20worst%20performance%20was%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20FY19%20when%20only%209%25%20of%20the%20target%20was%20achieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20April-June%202016%2C%20the%20scheme%20only%20achieved%2071%25%20of%20its%20target%2C%20followed%20by%20completion%20of%2075%25%20of%20the%20works%20in%20the%20following%20year%2C%20the%20business%20daily%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20April-September%202022%2C%20only%2041%25%20of%20the%20target%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmie.com%2Fkommon%2Fbin%2Fsr.php%3Fkall%3Dwarticle%26dt%3D20230130115811%26msec%3D626%5C%22%3Ecould%20be%20constructed%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20stipulated%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Statistics%20and%20Programme%20Implementation%20monitors%20the%20programme%E2%80%99s%20performance%20and%20considers%20it%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%E2%80%9D%20if%20it%20falls%20below%2080%25%20of%20its%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECurrently%20in%20its%20third%20phase%2C%20PMGSY%20focuses%20on%20consolidating%20the%20rural%20road%20network%20to%20connect%20agricultural%20markets%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20hospitals.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20a%20poverty-reduction%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20budget%20allocation%20for%20the%20programme%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbudget%2Funion-budget-2023-many-surprises-on-rural-development-front-9981821.html%5C%22%3Eremained%20the%20same%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Rs%2019%2C000%20crores%20in%20the%202023-24%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20the%20scheme%20had%20achieved%20its%20target%20was%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202015.%20It%20had%20surpassed%20its%20target%20by%20206%25%20and%20the%20total%20length%20of%20constructed%20roads%20stood%20at%2010%2C726%20km%20as%20against%20the%20targeted%205%2C200%20km%20in%20the%20quarter%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202005%2C%20PMGSY%20was%20a%20centrally%20sponsored%20scheme.%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-IN%5C%22%3EFrom%202015-16%2C%20the%20funding%20is%20being%20shared%20between%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20states%20in%20the%20ratio%20of%2060%3A40.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frwdbihar.gov.in%2FSchemePMGSY.aspx%5C%22%3Egovernment%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20primary%