%2C%20has%20been%20sidetracked%20in%20the%20decision-making%20process%20involving%20her%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20just%20the%20Captain%20of%20Ports%20department%20that%20is%20engaging%20in%20pressurising%20tactics%20to%20shoo%20away%20fishermen%20from%20fishing%20during%20the%20National%20Games%20but%20also%20the%20Goa%20Fisheries%20Department.%20Their%20personnel%20called%20up%20the%20All%20Goa%20Small%20Scale%20Responsible%20Fisheries%20Union%20(AGSSRFU)%20seeking%20assistance%20to%20clear%20the%20beach%20of%20all%20the%20canoes.%20%E2%80%9CFisheries%20department%20was%20set%20up%20to%20promote%20fishing%20but%20here%2C%20the%20department%20is%20sabotaging%20our%20interests%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20National%20Games%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%C2%A0%20fisherman%20Sanjay%20Pereira.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20fishing%20community%20here%20have%20been%20banned%20from%20accessing%20the%20sea.%20Pereira%20recalled%20that%20during%20the%20G20%20summit%20too%2C%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20shut%20down%20fishing%20activity%20for%20three%20days.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20Covid-19%20lockdown%2C%20we%20were%20stopped%20from%20carrying%20out%20fishing%20activities%20for%20over%2015%20days.%20And%20now%2C%20for%20National%20Games%2C%20they%20want%20fishermen%20to%20do%20away%20with%20their%20canoes%20for%2020%20days.%20How%20are%20we%20supposed%20to%20earn%20our%20livelihood%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2018%2C%20AGSSRFU%20president%20Shaila%20D%E2%80%99mello%20and%20secretary%20Laximan%20Mangueshkar%20submitted%20letters%20to%20the%20Captain%20of%20Ports%20as%20well%20as%20Director%20of%20Fisheries%20condemning%20the%20decision%20to%20shut%20down%20fishing%20activities%20in%20Zuari%20river%20and%20Arabian%20Sea.%20They%20called%20the%20decision%20a%20%E2%80%9Csuicidal%20adventure%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%207