d%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20a%20dismal%20placement%20record%20and%20absurdly%20short%20training%20programmes%2C%20where%20overzealous%20private%20players%20have%20replicated%20the%20public%20infrastructure%20of%20Industrial%20Training%20Institutes%2C%20instead%20of%20building%20upon%20it.%20This%20has%20happened%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20government%20think%20tank%20NITI%20Aayog%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fjobs%2Ffresher%2Fenabling-platforms-for-gig-workers-and-their-future%2Farticleshow%2F99081366.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ehad%20suggested%3C%2Fa%3E%20ways%20to%20resuscitate%20it%2C%20as%20recently%20as%20January%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Skill%20India%20and%20PMKVY%20are%20inadequate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20Rati%20Bhan%20ji%20again%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20for%20a%20plumbing%20consultation.%20I%20wanted%20to%20discuss%20with%20him%20India%E2%80%99s%20skill%20programmes.%20I%20wanted%20to%20understand%C2%A0why%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20find%20a%20good%20plumber%20when%20Rati%20Bhan%20ji%20is%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20114909%2Fimage0.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20114909%2Fimage0.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20114909%2Fimage0-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20114909%2Fimage0-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680962%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERati%20Bhan%20ji%2C%20a%20plumber%20since%201996%2C%20says%20to%20be%20able%20to%20work%20on%20site%2C%20independently%2C%20a%20plumber%20needs%20five%20years%20of%20training%20mixed%20with%20experience.%20Photo%20provided%20by%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20returned%20from%20Singapore%2C%20triggering%20class%20arrogance%20in%20me.%20He%20was%20on%20training%2C%20funded%20by%20a%20pipe%20company%20that%20wanted%20to%20put%20him%20in%20charge%20of%20a%20project%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%20training%20was%20not%20part%20of%20the%20Skill%20India%20mission%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmkvyofficial.org%2F%5C%22%3EPradhan%20Mantri%20Kaushal%20Vikas%20Yojana%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20was%20not%20a%20wasteful%20two-month%20course%20for%20newbies%2C%20ill-suited%20to%20take%20the%20rough%20and%20tumble%20of%20plumbing%2C%20who%20will%20drop%20out%20of%20the%20trade%20in%20no%20time.%20Out%20of%20ten%20plumbers%2C%20less%20than%20two%20trained%20by%20Skill%20India%20stick%20around%2C%20practitioners%20who%20source%20from%20the%20mission%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Singapore%20stint%20was%20training%20in%20best%20practices%20for%20Rati%20Bhan%20ji%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20plumber%20since%201996.%20He%20works%20on%20site%20with%20a%20team%20of%20senior%20and%20junior%20masons%2C%20and%20helpers%2C%20and%20labour.%20He%20is%20so%20experienced%20that%20he%20can%20detect%2C%20even%20from%20a%20description%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20where%20his%20team%20is%20getting%20stuck.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20kind%20of%20training%20is%20not%20provided%20in%20the%20Skill%20India%20syllabi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Plumbing%20Association%20told%20me%20the%20correct%20way%20of%20training%20new%20plumbers%3A%20it%20should%20be%20a%20modular%20course%20consisting%20of%20at%20least%20eight%20modules%2C%20stretching%20over%2015%20days%20each.%20The%20modules%20should%20not%20be%20taught%20in%20continuity%20because%20plumbers%2C%20after%20all%2C%20have%20to%20earn%20between%20their%20training.%20The%20