rtments%20struggling%20with%20waste%20disposal%20challenges.%20About%20200%20apartments%20and%20complexes%20in%20Kerala%20and%20Bengaluru%20have%20begun%20to%20dispose%20of%20their%20solid%20waste%2C%20both%20degradable%20and%20non-degradable%2C%20in%20a%20scientific%20and%20cost-effective%20way%20while%20promoting%20green%20earth.%20For%20this%2C%20Kenterra%20charges%20about%20Rs%20350%20per%20month%20per%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Manoj%20informs%20that%20they%20are%20able%20to%20manage%20about%2010%2C000%20kg%20of%20waste%20every%20day.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332642%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Manoj%20informs%20that%20they%20are%20able%20to%20manage%20about%2010%2C000%20kg%20of%20waste%20every%20day.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20these%20housing%20societies%20is%20the%20Link%20Valley%20Resident%20Association%20in%20Kochi.%20Home%20to%20at%20least%20400%20people%2C%20the%20housing%20society%20now%20converts%20close%20to%20100%20kg%20of%20biodegradable%20waste%20into%20compost%2C%20thanks%20to%20Kenterra.%3C%2Fp%3E