ontribute%20to%20a%20healthy%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20differentiates%20millets%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20thrive%20in%20harsh%20growing%20conditions%20and%20are%20climate%20resilient.%20They%20require%20much%20less%20water%20than%20grains%20like%20rice%20and%20wheat.%20The%20FAO%20says%20that%20millets%20provide%20antioxidants%2C%20minerals%2C%20fibre%2C%20iron%20and%20protein%2C%20alongside%20being%20gluten-free%20with%20a%20low-glycaemic%20index.%20They%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325105%2Fhyderabad-entrepreneur-raju-bhupati-makes-affordable-troo-good-millet-snacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeconomical%20for%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20require%20less%20water%20and%20fewer%20pesticides%2C%20becoming%20a%20boon%20to%20small%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMillets%20are%20India%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20food%20grain%2C%20grown%20across%20the%20country.%20They%20were%20sidelined%20over%20the%20years%2C%20but%20now%20the%20focus%20is%20squarely%20back%20on%20how%20one%20can%20use%20these%20grains%20in%20their%20diet%20and%20farmers%20are%20switching%20back%20to%20growing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20forefront%20of%20this%20change%20are%20Indians%20who%20are%20bringing%20millets%20back%20to%20the%20spotlight%20through%20their%20innovations.%20They%20are%20delivering%20millets%20in%20new%2C%20interesting%20ways%2C%20helping%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20five%20Indians%20championing%20the%20humble%20grain%20through%20their%20startups%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EVeer%20Shetty%20Biradar%2C%20SS%20Bhavani%20Foods%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20583px)%20100vw%2C%20583px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebet