onverted%20into%20a%20forum%20of%20listeners.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20how%20the%20Listener%E2%80%99s%20Army%20started.%20Today%20our%20non-profit%20is%20around%20600%20listeners%20strong%20who%20are%20all%20volunteers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20volunteers%20or%20listeners%20and%20the%20people%20who%20want%20to%20tell%20their%20stories%20are%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Pune%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELending%20a%20compassionate%20ear%20to%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20a%20person%20can%20become%20a%20listener%2C%20Raj%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20stories%20and%20incidents%20that%20people%20share%20can%20be%20quite%20taxing%20and%20overwhelming.%20This%20is%20why%20every%20person%20who%20wants%20to%20become%20a%20listener%20has%20to%20undergo%20a%20small%20evaluation%2C%20conducted%20by%20psychologists%20and%20therapists%20who%20collaborate%20with%20us.%20Once%20the%20volunteers%20are%20cleared%20by%20the%20therapist%2C%20we%20let%20them%20in%20our%20army%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22So%20far%2C%20Raj%20has%20amassed%20a%20following%20of%20more%20than%2018%2C000%20on%20Instagram.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C